lor: #008000;\">Main configuration parameters\'</span> AUTO_INCREMENT<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">=1</span> ;</em></p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\"><em>Default content</em></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Come from package script</p>'),('MT0.10',13,'ENG','tickets changelog','<p class=\"title\">Tickets and changelog</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can provide tickets changelog list to user.</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>Main&nbsp;table of tickets is&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:table_tickets/&gt;</strong></span></li>\n<li>Texts elements of tickets and documentation screens is in table&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:table_tickets_texts/&gt;</strong></span></li>\n<li>Translation of tickets class is in table&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:table_tickets_class/&gt;</strong></span></li>\n</ul>'),('MT0.10',14,'ENG','Properties list','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This section will list all features available to custom your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Technical Name</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Quick description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\" style=\"text-align: left;\" colspan=\"2\">Definition in each &lt;isys:appli/&gt;&nbsp;configuration file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\">&lt;ipage:21 __active_ticket/&gt;</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Enable direct access to tickets list</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\">&lt;ipage:22 __active_user_doc/&gt;</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Enable button to reach user documentation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>&lt;ipage:23 __active_tech_doc/&gt;</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>Enable button to reach technical documentation</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',15,'ENG','Main 