subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Write</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">define_attribute</span>(\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__id_theme</span>\', \'<span style=\"color: #808080;\">blue</span>\');</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Read</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">echo</span><strong> $my_object</strong>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">read_attribute</span>(\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__id_theme</span>\');</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">will return <span style=\"color: #808080;\">blue</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">default</span></p>'),('MT0.10',19,'ENG','Toolbar','<p class=\"title\">Description</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Toolbar is a area that regroup all button to send command on your list.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/tools_bar.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/tools_bar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"619\" height=\"312\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',20,'ENG','body','<p class=\"title\">Overview</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">The body screen part display results of your main query in list.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Body started from top with head columns row and ended bottom with the page navigation bar.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Width of body part is full from left to right.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/body_area.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/body_area.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',21,'ENG','version and tickets list link : [color=CadetBlue]__active_ticket[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Fonction</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Active or not direct link to list of <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt