"735\" height=\"322\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',103,'ENG','customize color column name : [color=CadetBlue]__column_name_group_of_color[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Description</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can customize column name to use &lt;ipage:100/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">if none name defined by used then a default name will recover from configuration table <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:table_config/&gt;</strong></span> index 9.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This default value is set to <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:9/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Standard</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\">__column_name_group_of_color</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Access&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Read Write</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Write</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">define_attribute</span>(\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__<span>column_name_group_of_color</span></span>\', \'<span style=\"color: #808080;\">MyColumnOfColorName</span>\');</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Read</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">echo</span><strong> $my_object</strong>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">read_attribute</span>(\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__<span>column_name_group_of_color</span></span>\');</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">will return<span style=\"color: #808080;\">&nbsp;MyColumnOfColorName</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:9/&gt;</strong></span></p>'),('MT0.10',104,'ENG','HTML position : [color=CadetBlue]__internal_HTML_position[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Fonction</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Setup HTML position mode of your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;i