p part of each column and have a search input box.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_part.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_part.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"364\" height=\"410\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',109,'ENG','column body part','<p class=\"title\">Column body part</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Body part content data of matched column query defined in your &lt;ipage:25main query/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Just under &lt;ipage:108/&gt;, column body part display data information of each field defined in your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_body_part.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_body_part.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"366\" height=\"414\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',110,'ENG','__CHECKBOX__','<p class=\"title\">Constante name</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">__CHECKBOX__</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">checkbox</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Usefull</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">in &lt;ipage:44 declare column/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',111,'ENG','Lov and sublisha setup','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This section will list all features available to custom sub lisha screen.</p>'),('MT0.10',112,'ENG','sort by order by  : [color=CadetBlue]define_column_lov_order[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Description</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Define order result by column priority in list of values.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">For severals order by, call severals time this function.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">First call define the highest priority and then priority decrease</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Function</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\">define_column_lov_order</span>(<span style=\"color: #888888;\">column_name</span>,<span style=\"color: #888888;\">order_mode</span>)</p>\n<p clas