e\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Comments</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`table1`.`id` AS `myid`,</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SUM(`table1`.`amount`)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">FROM</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`table1`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>GROUP BY</strong>&nbsp;`myid`</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SELECT&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`der`.`id` AS `myid`,</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span>`der`.</span>`tot` AS `total`</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">(</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">`table1`.`id`,</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">SUM(`table1`.`amount`) AS `tot`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">FROM</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">`table1`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\"><strong>GROUP BY</strong>&nbsp;`table1`.`id`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">)</span> der</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">WHERE 1 = 1</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Encapsulation of <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Group by</strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',115,'ENG','title area','<p class=\"title\">Column head title area</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This area below had 3 differents features.</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>Display column title</li>\n<li>Drag and drop zone to move column position</li>\n<li>Change or define a column order by ( Hold control key pressed to add new sub order by )</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_title_area.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_title_area.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"208\" height=\"122\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Setup</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To define title of column, you have to input title value in &lt;ipage44: column definition&gt; on fourth parameters as below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_title%20feature.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_title%20feature.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"835\" height=\"83\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">It\'s possible to have an empty title but features to move or order by column are still actives.</p>'),('MT0.10',116,'ENG','order by area','<p class=\"title\">Column head order by area</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This area below display order by option if any setup or forced by user.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_order_area.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_order_area.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"209\" height=\"122\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Ascending or Descending</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Descending mode means from the <span>smallest</span>&nbsp;to the <span>largest</span>. You can see this following icon.</p>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"__blue_ico_sort-ascend\" style=\"background-image: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); height: 20px; width: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"normal\">Ascending mode means from the largest to the smallest.&nbsp;<span>You can see this following icon.</span></p>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"__blue_ico_sort-descend\" style=\"background-image: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); height: 20px; width: 18px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"title\">Deep order</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have more than one sorted column then you will see a number as exponent.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">That number provide you priority of you order. Number one have the higest priority.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Order priority is automatically computed. It\'s the seqential order of function call &lt;ipage:95&nbsp;define_order_column/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below, description field is on the third call position. So priority order is set to three.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_order_priority.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_order_priority.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"543\" height=\"132\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Function</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To setup order by, use &lt;ipage:95 order column/&gt; function.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To remove order by option, use column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>By program setup, use constante &lt;ipage:117/&gt;</span></p>'),('MT0.10',117,'ENG','__NONE__','<p class=\"title\">Constante name</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">__NONE__</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&gt;&lt;</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Usefull</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">in function &lt;ipage:95 sort by column/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',118,'ENG','contextual menu','<p class=\"title\">Column head contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This area display information and provide interactive action with user.</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">Standard form</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">It\'s a free marble as below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_free_marble.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_free_marble.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"143\" height=\"96\" /></p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">Hover</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">That means there is standard contextual menu available.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you hover this area, you will see the following icon. That is actif if you left click on this area.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"204\" height=\"101\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have custom matchcode list on column, then a red marble will appears.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_red_marble.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_red_marble.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"143\" height=\"104\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">if some filter are turn on you have a different form</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_filter_on.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_filter_on.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"129\" height=\"110\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Setup</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To define title of column, you have to input title value in &lt;ipage44: column definition&gt; on fourth parameters as below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_title%20feature.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_title%20feature.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"835\" height=\"83\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">It\'s possible to have an empty title but features to move or order by column are still actives.</p>'),('MT0.10',119,'ENG','details menu','<p class=\"title\">Column head contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you right click on contextual button, a new contextual menu windows appears.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_details.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/column_head_context_menu_details.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"173\" height=\"205\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you left click on contextual menu button, custom or standard distinct values available on this column will appear.</p>'),('MT0.10',120,'ENG','date rules','<p class=\"title\">Wizard on column type date</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"normal\">if no date format defined on column then use default system date format depend on your localization.</p>'),('MT0.10',121,'ENG','quick search mode : [color=CadetBlue]__active_quick_search[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Description</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Active or not quick search on column head input area.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Quick search send request to server then you start to type something in column head input area.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have a huge table, this function can be slow and unefficient. So, you can disable it.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Function</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_quick_search</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Access&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Read Write</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Possible values</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">&nbsp;</span>: Quick search is on.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span>&nbsp;: Quick search if off.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Write</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">define_attribute</span>(\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_quick_search</span>\', <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span>);</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Read</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">echo</span><strong> $my_object</strong>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">read_attribute</span>(\'<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_quick_search</span>\');</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">will return <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>true</span></p>'),('MT0.10',1,'FRA','Accueil documentation technique','<p class=\"title\">Bienvenue sur la documentation technique</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Cette documentation est l&agrave; pour vous aider &agrave; mettre en place l\'objet&nbsp;<span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isym:lisha/&gt;</strong></span>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Voici les diff&eacute;rentes parties trait&eacute;es :</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>Comment &lt;ipage:2/&gt; votre <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isym:lisha/&gt;</strong></span>&nbsp;dans votre environnement de travail.</li>\n<li><span>&lt;ipage:14/&gt; complet de configuration pour&nbsp;</span><span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isym:lisha/&gt;</strong></span>.</span></li>\n<li><span>Les &lt;ipage:30/&gt;</span></li>\n<li><span>Principales fonctions internes &lt;ipage:59/&gt;</span></li>\n<li><span>&lt;ipage:93/&gt; de quelques d&eacute;fintions typique</span></li>\n</ul>'),('MT0.10',123,'ENG','Define column lov  : [color=CadetBlue]define_lov[/color]','<p class=\"title\">Description</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Initialization of customer list of value for a column defined in &lt;ipage:25 main query/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Function</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #008080;\">define_lov</span>(<span style=\"color: #888888;\">p_sql, p_title</span>, <span style=\"color: #888888;\">p_before_as</span>,<span style=\"color: #888888;\"> p_col_return</span>)</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Parameters</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Type</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>p_sql</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">string</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Define lov query using standard &lt;ipage:113/&gt;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>p_title</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">string</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>Define you lov title</p>\n<p><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_tech/picture/lov_title_area.png\')\" src=\"doc_tech/picture/lov_title_area.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"223\" height=\"163\" /></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>p_before_as</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">string</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>define part of return field before as</p>\n<p>Example if returned column is <strong>`mode`</strong>&nbsp;use &nbsp;<strong>TRANS2.`mode`</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">SELECT</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <strong>TRANS2.`mode`</strong></span> AS `mode`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\"> TRANS2.`text` AS `text`</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\"> FROM</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\"> `transaction2` TRANS2</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\"> WHERE 1 = 1</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\"> AND TRANS2.`mode` = \'||TAGLOV_mode**mode||\'</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>p_col_return</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">string</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>define part of return field by query ( after as part )</p>\n<p>Example if returned column is&nbsp;<strong>`mode`</strong>&nbsp;use <strong>mode</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">SELECT</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">TRANS2.`mode`&nbsp;AS <span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>`mode`</strong></span>,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">TRANS2.`text` AS `text`</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">FROM</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">`transaction2` TRANS2</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">WHERE 1 = 1</span><br /><span style=\"color: #c0c0c0;\">AND TRANS2.`mode` = \'||TAGLOV_mode**mode||\'</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"title\">Access&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">write</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">Write</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>$my_object</strong>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #008080;\">define_lov</span>(\" <span style=\"color: #808080;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\"> TRANS2.`mode` AS `mode`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #808080;\"> TRANS2.`text` AS `text`</span><br /><span style=\"color: #808080;\"> FROM</span><br /><span style=\"color: #808080;\"> `transaction2` TRANS2</span><br /><span style=\"color: #808080;\"> WHERE 1 = 1</span><br /><span style=\"color: #808080;\"> AND TRANS2.`mode` = \'||TAGLOV_mode**mode||\'</span>\",<br /> \'<span style=\"color: #808080;\">Title of description</span>\',<br /> \'<span style=\"color: #808080;\">TRANS2.`text`</span>\',<br /> \'<span style=\"color: #808080;\">text</span>\'<br /> );</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default value</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">No default value</p>'),('MT0.10',125,'ENG','[b][color=blue]FROM[/color][/b] manual output fields parsing','<p class=\"title\">Split manual output field</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">For performance reason, you have to split manualy output fields from the rest of your main query.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You have a specific string to use. That string is defined in your configuration table by index 10.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Split String</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Your current split string is :&nbsp;&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Mandatory</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This string is mandatory in your query.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Original query</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Lisha Query to write</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Comments</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>SELECT <span>`table1`.</span>`id` AS `myid` FROM `table1`;</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #808080;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #808080;\">`table1`.`id` AS `myid`</span></p>\n<p><span>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #808080;\">`table1`</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">WHERE 1 = 1</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Mark limit of output fields in query&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',126,'ENG','[b][color=blue]WHERE[/color][/b] always where condition','<p class=\"title\">WHERE conditions</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">if your query has no&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">WHERE</span>&nbsp;condition then&nbsp;ou have to add one at the end of your <span style=\"color: #000000;\">&lt;ipage:25 main query/&gt;</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Mandatory</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This string is mandatory in your query.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Original query</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Lisha Query to write</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Comments</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\"><span>SELECT <span>`table1`.</span>`id` AS `myid` FROM `table1`;</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #808080;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #808080;\">`table1`.`id` AS `myid`</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #808080;\">&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #808080;\">`table1`</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>WHERE 1 = 1</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>If no where condition in your query.</p>\n<p>Please add neutral one as below</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">WHERE 1 = 1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\">\n<p><span><span>SELECT&nbsp;</span><span>`table1`.</span><span>`id` AS `myid`</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>FROM `table1`</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>WHERE <span>`table1`.</span><span>`id` BETWEEN 30 AND 500</span>;</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\">SELECT&nbsp;`table1`.`id` AS `myid`\n<p><span>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</span></p>\n<p>`table1`</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">WHERE</span>&nbsp;`table1`.`id` BETWEEN 30 AND 500;</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>There is already and WHERE condition in your main query.</p>\n<p>Nothing special to do.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',127,'ENG','[b][color=blue]OUTPUT FIELDS[/color][/b] writing style','<p class=\"title\">Output fields writing format</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>You have to define each output field one by one.</li>\n<li>To have a good reading of your query, use one output field by row ( means carriage return in the end of your output field definition&nbsp;).</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"title\">Before as part</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Define what you will display in your query.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">After as part</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Keep in mind that after part will be name used to do update in your &lt;ipage:88 update table/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal blink_on\"><strong>after_as</strong>&nbsp;name have to get name as it\'s defined in your &lt;ipage:88 update table/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below we use an &lt;ipage:88 update table/&gt; named <strong>`BUG`</strong></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">`<strong>BUG</strong>`.`who` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>AS</strong></span>&nbsp;`<strong>who`</strong>, <span style=\"color: #008000;\">-- field `who` is defined in `BUG` table</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">`<strong>TEX</strong>`.`status` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>AS</strong></span>&nbsp;`<strong>mystatus`</strong>,&nbsp;<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #808080;\">-- `mystatus` : you can use any name because you display information not from &lt;ipage:88 update table/&gt;</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">`<strong>BUG</strong>`.`reference` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>AS</strong></span>&nbsp;`<strong>reference`</strong>,<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #008000;\">-- field `reference` is defined in `BUG` table</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">`<strong>BUG</strong>`.`Last_mod` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>AS</strong></span>&nbsp;`<strong>last_mod`</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #008000;\">-- field `last_mod` is defined in `BUG` table</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">....</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"normal\">Use</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span>`my_table1`.</span>`field1` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `myfield1`,</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span>`my_table3`.</span>`field4` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `myfield2`</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">...</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">instead of</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">*</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span>...</span></p>'),('MT0.10',128,'ENG','query limits have to encapsulate','<p class=\"title\">Main query limits</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">There are some restriction on your original query that you can\'t integrate in <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> as defined.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To use it without any error, you always can use query encapsulation.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below, a list of limits</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>&lt;ipage:129 GROUP BY/&gt;</li>\n<li>&lt;ipage:130 HAVING/&gt;</li>\n<li>&lt;ipage:131 UNION or UNION ALL/&gt;</li>\n</ul>'),('MT0.10',130,'ENG','[b][color=blue]HAVING[/color][/b]','<p class=\"title\">HAVING condition</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have to use a <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">HAVING</span> condition, please encapsulate your &lt;ipage:25 main query/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example :</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Original query</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Lisha Query to write</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Comments</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`table1`.`id` AS `myid`,</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SUM(`table1`.`amount`)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">FROM</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`table1`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>GROUP BY</strong>&nbsp;`myid`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>HAVING</strong> <span>SUM(`table1`.`amount`) &gt; 50</span>;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SELECT&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`der`.`id` AS `myid`,</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`der`.`tot` AS `total`</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">(</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">`table1`.`id`,</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">SUM(`table1`.`amount`) AS `tot`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">FROM</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">`table1`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\"><strong>GROUP BY</strong>&nbsp;`table1`.`id`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\"><strong>HAVING</strong> `tot` &gt; 5</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">)</span> der</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">WHERE 1 = 1</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Encapsulation of <strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Having</span></strong> and<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&nbsp;&lt;ipage:129 Group by/&gt;</strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',131,'ENG','[b][color=blue]UNION / UNION ALL[/color][/b]','<p class=\"title\">UNION or UNION ALL</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have to use a <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">UNION</span>&nbsp;or <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">UNION ALL</span> directive, please encapsulate your &lt;ipage:25 main query/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example :</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Original query</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Lisha Query to write</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Comments</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\" valign=\"top\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">\'0\' AS `A`</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">UNION ALL</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">\'1\' AS `A`&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">SELECT&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">`main`.`A` AS `output`</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:10/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">(</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">\'0\' AS `A`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">UNION ALL</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small; color: #808080;\">\'1\' AS `A`</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">)</span>&nbsp;`main`</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">WHERE 1 = 1</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">;</span></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Encapsulation of <strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">union</span></strong> or<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>&nbsp;union all</strong></span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',132,'ENG','Main configuration table','<p class=\"title\">Configuration table</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here we provide you advance explanation about configuration values that apply to all your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Parameters array&nbsp;</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Index</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Function / description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>1</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>ENG</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>Default main &lt;ipage:17/&gt; identifier</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>2</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">ID|ssid|VERSION|tab-level|LNG</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>Reserved keyword</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>3</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">28800&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>Page timeout in second</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>4</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">doc_user/picture/</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>path to user documentation pictures</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>5</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">doc_user/video/</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span>path to user documentation videos</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>6</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">doc_tech/picture/</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span>Path for technical documentation pictures</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>7</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>doc_tech/video/</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span>Path for technical documentation videos</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>8</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>f1</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span>String to use in your url to force customer view</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>9</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>GroupeTheme</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span>Default column name to use rows theme group</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>10</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>FROM -- #LISHA_MAIN_FROM_PARSING#</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span>String to split main string from output fields to other part</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>11</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>50000</span></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p><span>Max number of rows to export</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>');
