INSERT INTO `lisha_mt_doc_user_caption` VALUES ('MT0.10',1,'ENG','Lisha user documentation','<p class=\"title\">Purpose of user documentation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This user documentation try to help you to use <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> object.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">No technical knowledge are required.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Don\'t forgether to follow your feeling on feature. A lot of features are natural and friendly use. That a point we focus our effort.&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">How to use this documentation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You have two part in this documentation.</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>On your left, tree of documentation with engin search.</li>\n<li>On the right, detail of selected item in tree.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can simply click on vertical bar to switch between hide or show navigation tree as shown in following video.&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Example :</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><object width=\"721\" height=\"305\" data=\"doc_user/video/Howto_reduce_expand_treedoc.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/Howto_reduce_expand_treedoc.mov\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">Templates</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Please have a look to &lt;ipage:2/&gt; to help you using properly advanced features.</p>'),('MT0.10',2,'ENG','Templates','<p class=\"title\">Templates section</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">In this section, you can find some special template that you can use in your documentation.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Template are usefull to standardize your page and reach special string that provide to readers extra information.&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To discover special string format to use, you have to display page in update mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><object width=\"384\" height=\"288\" data=\"doc_user/video/howtosee_specialstring.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/howtosee_specialstring.mov\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\"><span>Example</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Here we are special string that provide you what is the current language in use</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Current language is :&nbsp;</span>&lt;ilocal:text/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',6,'ENG','page link','<p class=\"title\">configure page link</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Example :</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">jump to &lt;ipage:3/&gt; page</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>jump to &lt;ipage:3 my custom text/&gt; page</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:ssid/&gt;</strong></span></p>'),('MT0.10',7,'ENG','array','<p class=\"title\">Array with standard style</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"head_table\">\n<td>ID</td>\n<td>NAME</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row_table\">\n<td>&nbsp;12</td>\n<td>\n<p>Kitchen</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row_table\">\n<td>A7</td>\n<td>\n<p>Car</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row_table\">\n<td>John</td>\n<td>\n<p>Be good</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&lt;ilocalization/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',4,'ENG','picture','<p class=\"title\">Example of simple picture</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">First, put your picture in repository <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:5/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below an example of picture</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/example.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/example.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"179\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',5,'ENG','video','<p class=\"title\">Example of video inside your documentation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Put your movie into repository : <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:5/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Be carefull : Content of this video does\'nt matter.</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below, example with properties :</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>scale = aspect</li>\n<li>No loop</li>\n<li>autostart = <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span></li>\n<li>height = 50%</li>\n</ul>\n<p><object width=\"192\" height=\"240\" data=\"doc_user/video/test.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/test.mov\" /><param name=\"scale\" value=\"Aspect\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>&nbsp;Have to focus that this video does\'nt start when this page is displayed.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Other example with html inher property <span>autostart</span>&nbsp;is set to <strong>true</strong> just below ( video start immediately )</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>no scale option</li>\n<li>autostart = <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span></li>\n<li>loop = <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span></li>\n<li>custom height and width that truncate video window</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"normal\"><object width=\"192\" height=\"144\" data=\"doc_user/video/test.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/test.mov\" /><param name=\"loop\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"true\" /></object></p>'),('MT0.10',3,'ENG','Special string','<p class=\"title\">Examples of special dynamic strings</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Those string can provide you special information or action into your documentation.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Name of product : <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isym:lisha/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Language code in use :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:language/&gt;</strong></span>&nbsp;means <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;ilocal:text/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<div class=\"normal\">Full name of current Lisha version :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:version/&gt;</strong></span></div>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">Set of system information</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">URL Keyword + language in use :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:language_url/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Web browser in use : <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:browser/&gt;</strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">Technical information</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">MySQL version :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:MySQL/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Apache version :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:apache/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Php version :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:php/&gt;</strong></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"subtitle\">Display configuration setup value</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"normal\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</span></strong> configuration setup index 1 ( means default language system ) : &lt;LIconf:1/&gt;</li>\n<li class=\"normal\">localization configuration : &lt;ilocal:date_format/&gt;</li>\n<li class=\"normal\">MagicTree setup index 4 ( means Minimum string length to enable search in tree&nbsp;) : &lt;MTconf:4/&gt; digits</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"normal\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><br /></span></strong></p>'),('MT0.10',1,'FRA','Documentation utilisateur : Accueil','<p class=\"title\">Objectif de cette documentation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Ce document est cr&eacute;&eacute; pour vous aider &agrave; bien maitriser l\'objet&nbsp;<span>&lt;isym:lisha/&gt;</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Int&eacute;gration</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">C\'est une documentation int&eacute;gr&eacute;e qui affiche des informations directement li&eacute;es &agrave; votre environnement de travail.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Navigation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">L\'arborescence de la documentation vous permet de trouver rapidement sur un mot clef les pages portant sur la valeur cherch&eacute;e.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Glossaire</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Un &lt;ipage:16/&gt; est a votre disposition afin d\'&eacute;claircir le plus possible les termes les moins courants</p>'),('MT0.10',2,'FRA','Modèles','<p class=\"title\">Qu\'est ce qu\'un mod&egrave;le dans cette documentation ?</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Un mod&egrave;le est une chaine de caract&egrave;res sp&eacute;cifiques permettant d\'ex&eacute;cuter une action sp&eacute;ciale param&egrave;trable.</p>'),('MT0.10',3,'FRA','Information système','<p class=\"title\">Liste des informations syst&egrave;mes disponibles</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Nom usuel de l\'objet : <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isym:lisha/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Code de la langue actuellement utilis&eacute;e :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:language/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"normal\">Version technique&nbsp;:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:version/&gt;</strong></span></div>\n<p class=\"normal\">Navigateur web : <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:browser/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Services utilis&eacute;s :</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Version de MySQL :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:MySQL/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Version du serveur web :&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&lt;isys:apache/&gt;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Version g&eacute;n&eacute;rateur page dynamique ( php ) :&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&lt;isys:php/&gt;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Afficher un param&egrave;tre de configuration</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"normal\">De la &lt;isym:lisha/&gt; : param&egrave;tre d\'index 1 d&eacute;signant le code langue syst&egrave;me par d&eacute;faut : <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;LIconf:1/&gt;</strong></span></li>\n<li class=\"normal\">De cette documentation : param&egrave;tre d\'index 4 d&eacute;signant le nombre minimum de caract&egrave;res pour pouvoir lancer une recherche : <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;MTconf:4/&gt;</strong></span> caract&egrave;res</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"normal\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><br /></span></strong></p>'),('MT0.10',4,'FRA','image','<p class=\"title\">Format standard d\'une image</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Pour pouvoir ajouter une image, vous devez d\'abord la d&eacute;poser dans le r&eacute;pertoire<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&nbsp;&lt;LIconf:4/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Voici un exemple ci-dessous du rendu final de votre image sous le style &lt;image&gt; disponible des les styles de vos pages.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/example.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/example.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"415\" height=\"179\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',6,'FRA','Lien hypertext sur une page','<p class=\"title\">Exemple d\'un lien hypertext</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Voici le mod&egrave;le &agrave; utiliser pour cr&eacute;er un lien sur un noeud de l\'arborescence</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Aller &agrave; la page d\'&lt;ipage:3/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',5,'FRA','video','<p class=\"title\">Exemple de video</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Vous devez d&eacute;poser votre fichier video dans le r&eacute;pertoire<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&nbsp;&lt;LIconf:5/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><object width=\"384\" height=\"288\" data=\"doc_user/video/test.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/test.mov\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object></p>'),('MT0.10',7,'FRA','Tableau','<p class=\"title\">Exemple de tableau avec un style standard</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"head_table\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">ID</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Nom</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row_table\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">12</td>\n<td>\n<p>Cuisine</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row_table\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">A7</td>\n<td>\n<p>Voiture</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row_table\">\n<td>Pierre</td>\n<td>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Martin</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&lt;ilocalization/&gt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),('MT0.10',8,'ENG','Screen organization','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This section presents screen organization.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Main purpose of&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span><span>&nbsp;is to display masse information from query.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Theses information are listed by features in columns.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Each column have a header to gathering column information and a body to display data record set.</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\"><span>Overview</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/SRX_lisha_main_presentation.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/SRX_lisha_main_presentation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"241\" /></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Users can interact with each <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>&nbsp;using &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>'),('MT0.10',9,'ENG','Body result','<p class=\"title\">Body section</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This part will display to you information from query defined by your key user.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This part can scrowl on vertical and/or <span>horizontal</span>&nbsp;if space information data is too large for your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>&nbsp;size.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/SRX_main_body.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/SRX_main_body.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"333\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',10,'ENG','column header','<p class=\"title\">column head area</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Data are group by column.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Each column have a head area that provide you information and action to handle data display on &lt;ipage:9 body part/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/SRX_lisha_columns_head.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/SRX_lisha_columns_head.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"897\" height=\"443\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',11,'ENG','tool bar','<p class=\"title\">Main tool bar</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This area group each interactif button to send action on your&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</span></strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can have a &lt;ipage:41/&gt; looks and a <span>&lt;ipage:40/&gt;</span>&nbsp;looks.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Tool bar is always on top left&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>&nbsp;windows as shown below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/toolbar_location.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/toolbar_location.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"285\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Looks</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/toolbar_overview.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/toolbar_overview.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"486\" height=\"68\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">In this close screenshot above, we can see additional icon of user dans technical documentation.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This button depend on your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> configuration.</p>'),('MT0.10',12,'ENG','navigation bars','<p class=\"title\">Usefullness</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Display current page number and range of navigation page.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Display amount of rows depend on filtering option.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can also change current page displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">There is two position available ( top or bottom of &lt;ipage:9/&gt; part )</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below a&nbsp;&lt;isys:appli/&gt; with only bottom navigation bar.<img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/navigation_overview.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/navigation_overview.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"671\" height=\"253\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Another example with both ( top and bottom ) navigation bars<img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/navigation_overview_double.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/navigation_overview_double.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"676\" height=\"249\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',13,'ENG','version and ticket list link','<p class=\"title\">Extra information area</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This small area can provide you information about current lisha version and ( optional ) direct link to ticket list.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Current version</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You are using <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> version <strong>&lt;isys:version/&gt;</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/SRX_extra_area_information.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/SRX_extra_area_information.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"889\" height=\"434\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',14,'ENG','Language','<p class=\"title\">Language setup</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You have a general &lt;ipage:17/&gt; defined on your web page and your current language come from this <span>&lt;ipage:17/&gt;</span>&nbsp;group.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>&lt;ipage:17/&gt; key</span>&nbsp;is defined by a 3 digits string.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">French <span>&lt;ipage:17/&gt;</span>&nbsp;is defined by <strong>FRA</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">English <span>&lt;ipage:17/&gt;</span>&nbsp;is defined by <strong>ENG</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Default</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This default language is setup for once by your administrator.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">But, you can specify another language using URL directive ( see &lt;ipage:15/&gt;).</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Detection</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Your curent language used is&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;ilocal:text/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>'),('MT0.10',14,'FRA','Langue','<p class=\"title\">D&eacute;finir la langue</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Il existe deux niveaux pour d&eacute;terminer quelle langue sera utilis&eacute;e sur vos pages.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">La r&egrave;gle est toujours la m&ecirc;me.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">On part du plus d&eacute;taill&eacute; pour remonter vers le plus g&eacute;n&eacute;ral.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Une langue g&eacute;n&eacute;rale est d&eacute;finie par l\'administrateur. C\'est la langue qui a la plus faible priorit&eacute; et qui sera utilis&eacute;e que si aucune autre directive sp&eacute;cifique n\'est pr&eacute;cis&eacute;e.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">De fa&ccedil;on plus prioritaire, vous pouvez alors pr&eacute;ciser une autre langue au niveau de votre barre d\'adresse en utilisant la directive pr&eacute;vue &agrave; cette effet ( voir &lt;ipage:15/&gt;).</p>\n<p class=\"title\">D&eacute;tection de la langue courante</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">La langue actuellement utilis&eacute;e est le&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;ilocal:text/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>'),('MT0.10',15,'ENG','How to change language','<p class=\"title\">Force page language</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can change default language by using specific directive in your browser URL string.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Put in the end of your URL the following sequence : <em><span style=\"color: #808080;\">http://mydomaine/../my_page.php?ssid....</span></em>&amp;&lt;isys:language_url/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can use only &lt;ipage:17/&gt; &nbsp;come from this &lt;ipage:18 list/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">How to force english language using URL directive.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On this example below, key url language used is <strong>LNG</strong> but you may have different one on your system.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/url_force_english.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/url_force_english.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"602\" height=\"47\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',15,'FRA','Changer la langue','<p class=\"title\">Forcer une langue</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Vous pouvez changer la langue qu\'utilise par d&eacute;faut votre &eacute;cran en pr&eacute;cisant une directive dans l\'URL de votre navigateur web.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Exemple pour forcer en Fran&ccedil;ais.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/url_force_french.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/url_force_french.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"315\" height=\"96\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">La directive suit le mod&egrave;le suivant :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&amp;</strong></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:language_url/&gt;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Attention: si c\'est le premier param&egrave;tre de votre URL, vous devez mettre <strong>?</strong> comme sur la copie d\'&eacute;cran ci-dessus. Sinon, c\'est un <strong>&amp;</strong></p>'),('MT0.10',16,'ENG','Glossary','<p class=\"title\">Glossary</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This part describe specific work to be understanding by everyone.&nbsp;</p>'),('MT0.10',17,'ENG','Localization','<p class=\"title\">Expression</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Definition</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Localization define a group of country features.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This group contains :</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>language</li>\n<li>date format</li>\n<li>number format ( decimal and thousant symbol )</li>\n<li>currency unit</li>\n</ul>'),('MT0.10',18,'ENG','Available language','<p class=\"title\">List of available language</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Language feature is defined in &lt;ipage:17/&gt; group.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can use folowing ID code in your URL to change language ( Example:&nbsp;&lt;isys:language_url/&gt;&nbsp;).</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Current availables languages are :</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilocalization/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',18,'FRA','Langues disponibles','<p class=\"title\">Liste des langues disponibles</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">La langue provient d\'un groupe plus g&eacute;n&eacute;rale appel&eacute; &lt;ipage:17/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Utiliser le code ID du tableau ci-dessous pour forcer la localisation voulue ( Exemple:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:language_url/&gt;&nbsp;</strong></span>) et donc la langue qui sera employ&eacute;e.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Voici la liste des <span>&lt;ipage:17/&gt;</span>&nbsp;disponibles :</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilocalization/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',16,'FRA','Glossaire','<p class=\"title\">Glossaire</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Cette section d&eacute;finit les mots ou termes &eacute;tant particulier et difficile &agrave; appr&eacute;hender.</p>'),('MT0.10',17,'FRA','Localisation','<p class=\"title\">Expression</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Localisation</p>\n<p class=\"title\">D&eacute;finition</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Groupe de caract&eacute;ristiques d\'une application attach&eacute;s &agrave; une culture ou un pays.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Dans chaque localisation, on trouve :</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>La langue</li>\n<li>Le format de la date</li>\n<li>Le format des nombres</li>\n<li>Le symbole du s&eacute;parateur de millier</li>\n<li>Le symbole de la d&eacute;cimal</li>\n<li>La devise</li>\n</ul>'),('MT0.10',19,'ENG','change page number','<p class=\"title\">How to browse page results</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">By default, your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> display first page.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can change page in &lt;ipage:12/&gt; area by typing directly page number in page number field and valide.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/change_input_current_page_nulber.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/change_input_current_page_nulber.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"299\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If your input value is out of available range, then page will force to page max available.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Maxinum page number is next right of current page number input field as shown below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/navigation_page_max_range.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/navigation_page_max_range.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"155\" height=\"111\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',20,'ENG','navigation page limite','<p class=\"title\">Navigation page limite</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Low navigation page limit is always <strong>1</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">High navigation page limit depend on amount of rows is returned by filtering option and range of page.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This limit is automatically compute and display as shown below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/navigation_page_max_range.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/navigation_page_max_range.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"155\" height=\"111\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Unexpected input</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you input a non integer value, then page number will be forced to 1.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below some none interger input.</p>\n<p><object width=\"765\" height=\"300\" data=\"doc_user/video/weird_input_page_number.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/weird_input_page_number.mov\" /><param name=\"scale\" value=\"Aspect\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object></p>'),('MT0.10',21,'ENG','search','search'),('MT0.10',22,'ENG','column search operator','<p class=\"title\">Column search operator</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Operator is usefull to be more effective in your search and to reach faster right results.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Location</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">In each column contextual menu.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/search_column_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/search_column_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"204\" height=\"202\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Function</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Input values come from &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt; in &lt;ipage:10/&gt; area.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Your search request will be send by pressing enter or return key or pressing following refresh button</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -660px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">Full list of operator</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\">Operator name</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">Icon</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>&lt;ipage:65 Equal strict/&gt;</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -980px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Search only values that match exactly</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>&lt;ipage:66 like/&gt;</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1000px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Use &lt;ipage:38/&gt; to do an extended search</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>&lt;ipage:70 greather than/&gt;</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1020px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Only strict higher value</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>&lt;ipage:71 less than/&gt;</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1040px 0;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><span>Only strict lower value</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>......</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1040px 0;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',23,'ENG','global search','<p class=\"title\">Global search</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This feature is under construction.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Open a prompt window to enter string to search on every columns defined in your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Further details</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Have a look to &lt;ipage:57/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/global_search_button.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/global_search_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"137\" height=\"142\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',24,'ENG','full contextual menu','<p class=\"title\">Column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Each column have properties and user can change them.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">These properties are listed in contextual menu.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_contextual_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_contextual_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"243\" height=\"263\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Access</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To reach column contextual menu that provide you a way to change column properties, you have to click on left area of column &lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_contextual_menu_access.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_contextual_menu_access.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"188\" height=\"135\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can have no icon on this area. Just hover this area with your mouse and icon will appears.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Video example of how to reach contextual column menu</p>\n<p><object width=\"765\" height=\"300\" data=\"doc_user/video/column_contextual_menu.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/column_contextual_menu.mov\" /><param name=\"scale\" value=\"Aspect\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object></p>'),('MT0.10',25,'ENG','column','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Column display you data depending of filterying option in &lt;ipage:10/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Column have two main part</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>&lt;ipage:34/&gt;</li>\n<li>&lt;ipage:39/&gt;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_overview.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_overview.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"499\" height=\"588\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',26,'ENG','column features','<p class=\"title\">Columns features</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can manage all columns features using column feature button.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_main_features.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_main_features.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"183\" height=\"158\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">List</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\">Name</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">looks</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>Sort</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -600px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Define kind of sort of data</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Search mode</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -580px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Strict or extended</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>Alignment</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -760px 0;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<p>Left, right or center</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>Matchcode list</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -680px 0;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Matchcode list</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',27,'ENG','move column position','<p class=\"title\">Move column position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can move position of each column in your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Action</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To move a column, just hold left mouse button on column title and move it to final position mark by up and down red arrows.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p><object width=\"765\" height=\"265\" data=\"doc_user/video/move_column_position.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/move_column_position.mov\" /><param name=\"scale\" value=\"Aspect\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object></p>'),('MT0.10',28,'ENG','special format','<p class=\"title\">Column special format</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Column can be define with special data type.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can have :</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>&lt;ipage:31/&gt;</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Column format will add new control and action on your column.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">A column on format date will have extra calendar sub option like below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_date_extra_contextual_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_date_extra_contextual_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"223\" height=\"236\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',29,'ENG','hide column','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can hide columns defined in your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">From contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can only <span style=\"color: #993300;\">&lt;ilisha:20/&gt;</span> from &lt;ipage:24/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/hide_column_contextual_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/hide_column_contextual_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"249\" height=\"253\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">From columns features screen</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Mass columns features managment using columns features.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">A checked check box means that column is displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/columns_managment_features_display.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/columns_managment_features_display.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"544\" height=\"412\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Exception</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can\'t hide a default focus column.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">if you try to hide default focus column then the following error will raise</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/eng_error_message_hide_focused_column.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/eng_error_message_hide_focused_column.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"513\" height=\"338\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',30,'ENG','show or display column','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To display hidden columns defined in your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can do it only from&nbsp;<span>columns features managment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">A checked check box means that column is displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/columns_managment_features_display.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/columns_managment_features_display.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"544\" height=\"412\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',31,'ENG','date format','<p class=\"title\">Column with date format</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">A column on format date will have extra calendar sub option like below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_date_extra_contextual_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_date_extra_contextual_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"223\" height=\"236\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Date format</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Date format depend on your &lt;ipage:17/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Your current date format pattern is <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;ilocal:date_format/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Kick access to open calendar</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Right click in input box as shown below in video.</p>\n<p><object width=\"765\" height=\"300\" data=\"doc_user/video/column_date_quick_calendar.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"doc_user/video/column_date_quick_calendar.mov\" /><param name=\"scale\" value=\"Aspect\" /><param name=\"autoplay\" value=\"false\" /></object></p>'),('MT0.10',32,'ENG','numeric format <todo>','<p class=\"title\">numeric format</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Under construction...</p>'),('MT0.10',33,'ENG','marble','<p class=\"title\">Purpose of marble</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Marble is a mark <span>on each column</span>&nbsp;to show you quick information about match code list.</p>\n<p class=\"title\"><span>Localization</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>On the left of each header column input box.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/marble_localization.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/marble_localization.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"605\" height=\"96\" /></span></p>\n<p class=\"title\"><span>Stats</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>There are tree stats for marble.</span></p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\">Stats</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">looks</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>no marble</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">There is a no available list because there is a no&nbsp;<span>solvable dependance with another column</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\">white</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -180px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Default distinct value on this column.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\">red</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -700px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">Custom distinct value setup on this list.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span><br /></span></p>'),('MT0.10',56,'ENG','Clear filter and restore view','<p class=\"title\">Restore view</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Left click on this button will restore default view as defined by your key user or by an url directive.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">That means if you have some url directive defined then you will restart from position define in.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/restore_button_position_in_toolbar.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/restore_button_position_in_toolbar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"256\" height=\"92\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -320px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">Restore</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">What is restored ?</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>All columns properties</li>\n<li>navigation page position is set to 1</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"title\">Check</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">No special control.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:5/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',34,'ENG','head','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Head of column display general information about data to display.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This area provide you severals way to modify column looks and how to display his data.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of each column.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below an example with &lt;ipage:24/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_head.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_head.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"389\" height=\"309\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',35,'ENG','title','<p class=\"title\">Column title</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Each column have a title that give a data name to display.</p>\n<p class=\"title\"><span>Localization</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Into &lt;ipage:25/&gt;&lt;ipage:34/&gt; area.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of &lt;ipage:25/&gt; area.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_text_header.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_text_header.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"774\" height=\"120\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can also have no text to display.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_no_header_name.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_no_header_name.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"316\" height=\"303\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',36,'ENG','sort order mode','<p class=\"title\">Column data sort</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can sort a column by left clicking on his &lt;ipage:35/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the left of &lt;ipage:25/&gt;&lt;ipage:35/&gt;. Here below, we are on column called Caption and data are ascending sort.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_order_asc.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_order_asc.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"198\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Kind of sort</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\">Sort by</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">looks</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>&lt;ipage:67 Ascending/&gt;</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -600px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">From lower to higher value.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>&lt;ipage:68 Descending/&gt;</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -640px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">From higher to lower values.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>&lt;ipage:69 No sort/&gt;</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">None sort on this column.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>Sub priority</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -600px 0;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><sup>1</sup></span></div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">1 have higher priority.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below, column <strong>Upper</strong>&nbsp;has no sort.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_no_sort.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_no_sort.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"178\" height=\"185\" />&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here a lower to highter value.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_ascending_sort.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_ascending_sort.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"137\" height=\"156\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below, three sort with sub priority.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Highest priority is 1.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If there is no exponent number attach to sort icon that means no multi sort.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">High sort priority on <strong>Caption</strong> column then on <strong>date</strong>&nbsp;and finally&nbsp;<strong>normal</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_priority_order.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_priority_order.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"373\" height=\"159\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',37,'ENG','input box','<p class=\"title\">Column input box</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Input box of column is used to do two things.</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>Search</li>\n<li>Input data</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">In &lt;ipage:25/&gt;&lt;ipage:34/&gt;, just under column &lt;ipage:35/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_input_box.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_input_box.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"157\" height=\"133\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',38,'ENG','Jocker digit','<p class=\"title\">Expression</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Use a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">jocker digit</span> on search</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Definition</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">In database context, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">jocker digit</span> means special digit that provide you fonctionnal behaviour instead of his value.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">In MySQL database, <strong>%</strong>&nbsp;( percent ) means a random string and <strong>_</strong> ( underscore ) means a random digit.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">I want to search result contains string <strong>marble</strong>, i have to use string <strong>%marble%</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;</p>'),('MT0.10',39,'ENG','body','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Body of column display data information of each occurence.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This area provide you core data infromation.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Localization</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Just under &lt;ipage:25/&gt;&lt;ipage:34/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Here below an example of data column.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_body_core_data.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_body_core_data.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"205\" height=\"410\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',40,'ENG','Display mode','<p class=\"title\">What is this mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Display mode is use to only display information in &lt;ipage:9/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">No data updating available</p>\n<p class=\"title\">At a glance</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you don\'t see any edition button in &lt;ipage:11/&gt; that means you are in displya mode.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Juste under, example of a display mode lisha.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" src=\"doc_user/picture/display_mode_available.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"217\" height=\"112\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',41,'ENG','Update mode','<p class=\"title\">What is this mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This mode provide you full access to data ( read and write ) displayed in &lt;ipage:9/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">At a glance</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you see edition button in &lt;ipage:11/&gt; that means you are in update mode.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Juste under, example of a update mode lisha.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" src=\"doc_user/picture/update_mode_available.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"274\" height=\"112\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',42,'ENG','add or record a new line','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Left click on this button will attempt to record a new line with data input in each &lt;ipage:25/&gt;&lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can add only one new line by action.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Your have to be in &lt;ipage:41/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your &lt;isys:appli/&gt; in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: 0 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">Check</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">All check will be perform before recording line.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:6/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',43,'ENG','Help','<p class=\"title\">Help system</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can learn by practice in <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>. You do operation and then cancel it.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">But, sometimes you gain time to have a quick support on action or information displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You have two main ways to reach documentation support on this software.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Flying your mouse hover an area will display message in &lt;ipage:46/&gt; area.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">User documentation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You are currently in the user documentation.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Technical documentation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can reach technical documentation <a href=\"indextech.php\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Contextual help</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Available in &lt;isys:appli/&gt; screen when you flying hover any area. Then press on your keyboard <strong>CTRL(fn) + F11</strong>.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/help_shortcut.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/help_shortcut.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"583\" height=\"284\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">See &lt;ipage:44/&gt; for further details.</p>'),('MT0.10',44,'ENG','Contextual help','<p class=\"title\">Contextual help</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This help means that you can reach direct help page linked to your last move.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>You can call contextual help using key shortcut<strong> CTRL(fn) + F11</strong> when your mouse is hover any area.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Position</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>On the right of &lt;ipage:11/&gt;</span></p>'),('MT0.10',45,'ENG','Global help','Global help'),('MT0.10',46,'ENG','quick help message','<p class=\"title\">Quick help message</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This area displa