repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -500px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>Update available</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row_table\">\n<td>\n<div style=\"opacity: 0.25; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -500px 0;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>No update available because not line seletec</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p class=\"title\">Check</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">All check will be perform before updating lines.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #993300;\">&lt;ilisha:7/&gt;</span></p>'),('MT0.10',55,'ENG','tool bar','<p class=\"title\">Main action</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This section will describe all button always available in tool bar.</p>'),('MT0.10',50,'ENG','with selected line(s)','<p class=\"title\">Line(s) selected</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">That means you are in main &lt;ipage:41/&gt; with at least one line <span>selected</span>&nbsp;in &lt;ipage:9/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ipage:49 Edit button/&gt; and &lt;ipage:48 deletion button/&gt; are availables.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Looks</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/update_mode_selected_line.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/update_mode_selected_line.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"515\" height=\"283\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',51,'ENG','No line selected','<p class=\"title\">No line selected</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">That means you are in main &lt;ipage:41/&gt; but no line are selected for &lt;ipage:49 update/&gt; or &lt;ipage:48 deletion/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Looks</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/update_mode_no_line_selected.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/update_mode_no_line_selected.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"390\" height=\"231\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',52,'ENG','update line','<p class=\"title\">Updating in progress</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You just have pressed &lt;ipage:49 update button/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:apppli/&gt;</strong></span> display to you selection on which modification will be performed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">That means you are in main &lt;ipage:41/&gt; with at least one line <span>selected</span>&nbsp;in &lt;ipage:9/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ipage:12/&gt; vanish because no page navigation available during updating lines.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Tips</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">2 new icons action appears in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Looks</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/updating_lines_in_progress.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/updating_lines_in_progress.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"362\" height=\"191\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',53,'ENG','abort edition','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Left click on this button will abort current &lt;ipage:41/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This will discard all update you have input in &lt;ipage:10/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Your are in &lt;ipage:41/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your &lt;isys:appli/&gt; in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/cancel_update_button_toolbar.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/cancel_update_button_toolbar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"267\" height=\"114\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -200px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:78/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',54,'ENG','save lines update','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Record all selected lines with input information&nbsp;<span>in&nbsp;</span><span>&lt;ipage:10/&gt;</span><span>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Caution :</strong></span> Only checked box column will be updated.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Here below an example of checkbox to involved column in update (Only data from column <strong>datum</strong> and <strong>Mymodule</strong> will be used to update lines ).</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/checkbox_to_involved_column_in_update.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/checkbox_to_involved_column_in_update.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"492\" height=\"127\" /></span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Checkbox behaviour</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">When you start to type something in input box then update checkbox will switch on.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Available</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This button is only available in &lt;ipage:41/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your &lt;isys:appli/&gt; in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&nbsp;<img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/save_lines_button.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/save_lines_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"254\" height=\"129\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -960px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:50/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',57,'ENG','Multi column search','<p class=\"title\">Global search</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Left click on this button will perform a full search on each column defined in your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"blink_on\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">This function is not available (under construction)</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" src=\"doc_user/picture/toolbar_location.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"285\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -580px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">Check</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">No special control. All data will be displayed after this action.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:0/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',58,'ENG','Updating in progress','<p class=\"title\">What is this mode ?</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You have selected rows to do some update&nbsp;in &lt;ipage:41/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You have pressed &lt;ipage:49/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Your &lt;ipage:55/&gt; looks as below :</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/updating_in_progress_toolbar.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/updating_in_progress_toolbar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"184\" height=\"33\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',59,'ENG','No updating','<p class=\"title\">Mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">When you are not in updating mode.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This mode show you that kind of &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/not_updating_tool_bar.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/not_updating_tool_bar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"291\" height=\"134\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',60,'ENG','limited contextual menu','<p class=\"title\">Limited contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">When you are updating rows, navigation and some more option aren\'t available in column.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">In edit mode, you can\'t order column result.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Why this choice ?</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To avoid any mistake, a good way is to first do your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> looks change and then do your rows update.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">So, that means you only have acces to distinct or custom lov value in update mode using left click.&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Access</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">To reach column specific value available, you have to right click on area as below.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_contextual_menu_access.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_contextual_menu_access.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"188\" height=\"135\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/column_lov_values.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/column_lov_values.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"327\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',61,'ENG','Export','<p class=\"title\">Export list</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This button will export in CSV charset UTF-8 your list as displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span>Hidden columns will not be exported.</span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span><br /></span></p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Caution :</strong></span> If you check some rows then only checked rows will be exported.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">It\'s a best way to be more specific on your export selection.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Where to find this button ?</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/export_button_location.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/export_button_location.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"274\" height=\"112\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Available</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This button is not available in &lt;ipage:41/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Symbol</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -340px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">Confirmation</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You always have a confirmation popup to proceed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/export_popup_confirmation.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/export_popup_confirmation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"191\" /></p>\n<p class=\"normal\">if you reach export limit, you have that kind of message.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/export_limit_confirmation_popup.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/export_limit_confirmation_popup.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"413\" height=\"182\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Export limit</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">There is a limit to export rows to protect server service from crash.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This limit is currently set on your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> configuration to&nbsp;<span><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">&lt;LIconf:11/&gt;&nbsp;</span></strong>rows.</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:9/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',62,'ENG','Load customer filter','<p class=\"title\">Load customer preferences</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This bouton will display you list of current recorded preferences related to your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>&lt;isys:appli/&gt;</strong></span> in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/load_preference_button_in_toolbar.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/load_preference_button_in_toolbar.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"107\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -380px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">What is loaded ?</p>\n<ul class=\"normal\">\n<li>All columns properties ( filtering, order, position, hide or display )</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"title\">Check</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">No special control.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:4/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',63,'ENG','blink','<p class=\"title\">Special class to use</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;p class=\"<strong>blink_on</strong>\" style=\"text-align: center;\"&gt;&lt;span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"&gt;This action is not available&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"blink_on\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">example</span></p>'),('MT0.10',64,'ENG','Record user preferences','<p class=\"title\">Purpose</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Record looks and current filters option under a specific name<span>.</span></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Position</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">On the top of your &lt;isys:appli/&gt; in &lt;ipage:11/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" src=\"doc_user/picture/record_preferences_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"289\" height=\"123\" /></p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -560px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">&lt;ipage:46/&gt;</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">&lt;ilisha:50/&gt;</p>'),('MT0.10',65,'ENG','strict operator','<p class=\"title\">Strict search mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This mode will search exact string in column as typed into &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:34/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -980px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">In column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have already selected option, it\'s greyed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/Operator_equal_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/Operator_equal_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"328\" height=\"291\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',66,'ENG','like or as operator','<p class=\"title\">Extended search mode</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">This mode will search string in column using &lt;ipage:38/&gt; into &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:34/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1000px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">In column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have already selected option, it\'s greyed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/Operator_like_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/Operator_like_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"313\" height=\"253\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',67,'ENG','Ascending sort','<p class=\"title\">Ascending sort</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Sort data from the lowest to the higest value.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Caution</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can have priority on search column with an exponential number. The lower value have the higest priority.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example of sub priority</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\">Sort by</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">looks</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>Sub priority</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -600px 0;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><sup>1</sup></span></div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">1 have higher priority.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',68,'ENG','Descending sort','<p class=\"title\">Descending sort</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Sort data from the higest to the lower value.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Caution</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">You can have priority on search column with an exponential number. The lower value have the higest priority.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Example of sub priority</p>\n<table class=\"main_table\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"title\">\n<td class=\"head_table\">Sort by</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">looks</td>\n<td class=\"head_table\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"row_table\"><em>Sub priority</em></td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -600px 0;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><sup>1</sup></span></div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"row_table\">1 have higher priority.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>'),('MT0.10',69,'ENG','None sort option','<p class=\"title\">None sort option</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">There is no sort on your column.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">That means that output order will be randomize and drive by your database optimizer.</p>'),('MT0.10',70,'ENG','greather than operator','<p class=\"title\">Greather than operator</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Will return only greather values from string in &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:34/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1020px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">In column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have already selected option, it\'s greyed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/Operator_greather_than_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/Operator_greather_than_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"302\" height=\"245\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',71,'ENG','less than operator','<p class=\"title\">Less than operator</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Will return only lower values to string in &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:34/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1040px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">In column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have already selected option, it\'s greyed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/Operator_less_than_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/Operator_less_than_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"279\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',72,'ENG','greather than or equal operator','<p class=\"title\">Greather than or equal operator</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Will return only greather or equal values from string in &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:34/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1060px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">In column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have already selected option, it\'s greyed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/Operator_greather_than_or_equal_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/Operator_greather_than_or_equal_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"314\" height=\"251\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',73,'ENG','less than or equal operator','<p class=\"title\">Less than or equal operator</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Will return only lower or equal values to string in &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:34/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt;.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1080px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">In column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have already selected option, it\'s greyed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/Operator_less_than_or_equal_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/Operator_less_than_or_equal_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"318\" height=\"253\" /></p>'),('MT0.10',74,'ENG','is null operator','<p class=\"title\">Use is null operator</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">Will return null entries if exists. String in &lt;ipage:25/&gt; &lt;ipage:34/&gt; &lt;ipage:37/&gt; is <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">not used</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"title\">Icon</p>\n<div style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background: url(\'images/icons/img_16.png\'); background-position: -1100px 0;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"title\">In column contextual menu</p>\n<p class=\"normal\">If you have already selected option, it\'s greyed.</p>\n<p class=\"normal\"><img class=\"image\" onclick=\"window.open(\'doc_user/picture/Operator_is_null_menu.png\')\" src=\"doc_user/picture/Operator_is_null_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"314\" height=\"249\" /></p>');
