INSERT INTO `bugsreports` VALUES (1,101,'display',51,'1.00','2012-12-13 00:00:00','Add group of colors depend on column value','<p>Column name that carried color group had a default value record in configuration table index 9.</p>\n<p>You can customize this name using the standard method&nbsp;<a href=\"../indextech.php?id=103\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>By default, if your <a href=\"../indextech.php?id=25\" target=\"_blank\">main query</a>&nbsp;doesn\'t have column with this name, you will have only one set of color.</p>\n<p>Default color name group is zero ( 0 ).</p>\n<p>Please use index group color name except zero to avoid confusion.</p>','<p>Define a column value that carried group of color to display</p>\n<p>Exemple : Define column color that can return 0, 1 or 2</p>\n<p>0 will design set of color 0</p>\n<p>1 will design set of color 1</p>\n<p>and so on..</p>\n<p>Final result expected was a list with group of 3 differents color set.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-03 12:43:20',NULL),(2,100,'General',52,'1.00','2012-12-13 00:00:00','Translate object name vimofy to lisha','','<p>global code pass to move vimofy to lisha name of object !</p>','SRX',2,'2013-01-17 10:54:42',NULL),(3,100,'General',51,'1.00','2012-12-14 00:00:00','Normalization of javascript code !','<p>Still in progress...</p>','<p>Model of javascript header function !</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">/**==================================================================</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">&nbsp;* MT_selected_item: Called when item is selected in tree</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">&nbsp;* @evt : catch event&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">&nbsp;* @internal_id : Tree id root</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">&nbsp;* @row_id : Node unique identifier</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">&nbsp;* @mode : U : Update,D : Display</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">&nbsp;* @refresh : D : means reload tree with focus</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">&nbsp;====================================================================*/</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">function </span><span>MT_selected_item</span><span>(</span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">evt</span><span>,</span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">internal_id</span><span>,</span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">row_id</span><span>,</span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">mode</span><span>,</span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\">refresh</span><span>)</span></p>\n<p>{</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;...</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #cc99ff;\">//==================================================================</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #cc99ff;\">// Setup Ajax configuration</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #cc99ff;\">//==================================================================</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">....</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">var</span> <span>conf</span> <span>=</span>&nbsp;[]<span>;</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #cc99ff;\">//==================================================================</span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p>}</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #339966;\">/**==================================================================*/</span></p>','SRX',3,'2013-09-13 06:14:52',NULL),(4,101,'Documentation',52,'1.00','2012-12-14 00:00:00','Add magic tree for user documentation','<p>Internal parameters to hide / display this button</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">$obj_lisha_tran-&gt;<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>display_help_button</strong></span>(<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span>);&nbsp;// Display user documentation button</span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>','<p>Add a button to go to user documentation in toolbar</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/toolbar_user_documentation_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"174\" height=\"144\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-02-25 15:18:47',NULL),(5,101,'Documentation',51,'1.00','2012-12-14 00:00:00','Add magic tree for technical documentation','<p>Internal parameters to hide / display this button</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">$obj_lisha_tran-&gt;<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>display_tech_help_button</strong></span>(<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span>);&nbsp;// Display technical documentation button</span></p>','<p>Add a button to go to technical documentation in toolbar</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/toolbar_tech_documentation_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"215\" height=\"129\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-02-25 15:20:42',NULL),(6,100,'General',51,'1.00','2012-12-18 00:00:00','Split language text for screen into specific table in database','','<p>2 kind of tables</p>\n<ul>\n<li>General lisha text : lisha_text ( mandatory )</li>\n<li>Text for documentation and ticket screen :&nbsp;lisha_extra_screen_text ( optional )</li>\n</ul>','SRX',2,'2013-01-17 19:37:18',NULL),(7,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-01-17 00:00:00','Regroup all parameters into one file configuration','<p>Example of configuration.php file for package <strong>lisha1.00</strong></p>\n<p>&lt;?php</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_APPLICATION_RELEASE__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha1.00\"<span>);</span>// Lisha package name in use</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>// General database connexion</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_DATABASE_HOST__\"<span>,</span>\"localhost\"<span>);</span>// Host</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_DATABASE_SCHEMA__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha\"<span>);</span>// Schema</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_DATABASE_USER__\"<span>,</span>\"xxxxx\"<span>);</span>// user</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_DATABASE_PASSWORD__\"<span>,</span>\"xxxxx\"<span>);</span>// password</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>// Define lisha main tables</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_TABLE_FILTER__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha_filter\"<span>);</span>// Record custom view</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_TABLE_SETUP__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha_config\"<span>);</span>// General configuration</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_TABLE_LANGUAGE__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha_language\"<span>);</span>// Liste of language available</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_TABLE_TEXT__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha_text\"<span>);</span>// Text for internal use</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>// Define Tree documentation tables ( Optional )</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>// Text for documentation and tickets screen</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__LISHA_TABLE_EXTRA_TEXT__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha_extra_screen_text\"<span>);</span>// Text for documentation and tickets screen</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>// User documentation tree table ( Optional )</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__MT_TABLE_USER_DOCU__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha_mt_doc_user\"<span>);</span>// User tree documentation</p>\n<p><span>define(</span>\"__MT_TABLE_USER_DOCU_CAPTION__\"<span>,</span>\"lisha_mt_doc_user_caption\"<span>);</span>// User tree documentation caption</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>// Technical documentation tree table ( Optional )</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span>$path_root_lisha </span><span>=&nbsp; __LISHA_APPLICATION_RELEASE__;</span>// Internal use for tickets screen. Don\'t remove please</p>\n<p>?&gt;</p>','<p>To install package of lisha, you have to do 3 things</p>\n<ul>\n<li>copy file package into your web root site</li>\n<li>import lisha tables</li>\n<li>setup file into your_root_web_site/includes/lishaSetup/configuration.php</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-01-17 19:34:18',NULL),(8,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-01-17 00:00:00','New feature : Display or hide help button in tool bar','<p><span>By default, this help button is displayed</span></p>\n<p><span>That means you provide acces to tree of user documentation</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span>To hide this button,&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><em>$your_id_lisha</em></span><span>-&gt;<strong>display_help_button</strong>(</span><span>false</span><span>); </span>// Don\'t display help button</p>\n<p>To display this button,</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><em>$your_id_lisha</em></span>-&gt;<strong>display_help_button</strong>(true);&nbsp;// Display help button</p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p>don\'t call attribut function&nbsp;<strong>display_help_button</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>We speak about this button shown as just below</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_help_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"221\" height=\"103\" /></p>\n<p>You can display or hide this button by using parameters :&nbsp;<strong>display_help_button</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Example : </strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><em>$your_id_lisha</em></span>-&gt;display_help_button(false); // Don\'t display help button</p>','SRX',2,'2013-01-17 20:11:12',NULL),(9,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-01-17 00:00:00','New feature : Enable or disable ticket link','<p>Use following parameters</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><em>$your_id_lisha</em></span>-&gt;<strong>tickets_link_enable</strong>(<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span>);&nbsp;// disable tickets link</p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><span><em>$your_id_lisha</em></span>-&gt;<strong>tickets_link_enable</strong>(<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span>);&nbsp;// Display help button</p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p>don\'t call attribut function&nbsp;<strong>tickets_link_enable</strong></p>','<p>Here below, example of package <strong>lisha1.00</strong>.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><em>$your_id_lisha</em></span>-&gt;tickets_link_enable(<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span>); <span>// disable tickets link</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_tickets_link.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"156\" height=\"107\" /></p>\n<p>Warning : Version of package will always displayed, just link is enable or disable to jump to ticket screen&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-01-17 20:21:18',NULL),(10,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-01-17 00:00:00','Default language is hard coded with FRA','','<p>Use default language from <strong>config</strong> table index 1</p>','SRX',2,'2013-01-17 21:13:05',NULL),(11,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-01-17 00:00:00','Move hard coded text of calendar into database text table and load only language in use','<p>Following keyword</p>\n<p>SRX_CALENDAR_LANGUAGE</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Add all day of week, month in database text and remove hard coded code</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Important note :</strong></span> Index of start</p>\n<p><span>$_SESSION</span>[<span>$this</span>-&gt;c_ssid][<span>\'lisha\'</span>][<span>\'lib\'</span>][<span>$i</span>+<span>99</span>]</p>\n<p>$_SESSION<span>[</span><span>$this</span><span>-&gt;c_ssid][</span><span>\'lisha\'</span><span>][</span><span>\'lib\'</span><span>][</span>$actual_month<span>+</span><span>80</span><span>]</span></p>\n<p>$_SESSION<span>[</span><span>$this</span><span>-&gt;c_ssid][</span><span>\'lisha\'</span><span>][</span><span>\'lib\'</span><span>][</span>$day_of_date<span>+</span><span>92</span><span>]</span></p>','<p>Internal improvement</p>\n<p>Remove hard coded code</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-28 09:43:35','SRX_CALENDAR_LANGUAGE'),(12,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-01-18 00:00:00','Manage hide and display columns','<p>Clean lisha internal table using timeout of field tlu</p>\n<p>delete all lines where tlu &gt; lisha_config id 3 ( default 28800 seconds )</p>','<p>Add new feature to show or hide column with a new lisha to manage full list of column available</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Forbidden to hide all columns or protect js error on column size computing</li>\n<li>Reset button restore hide or show column features</li>\n<li>Add new memory table to store columns property and use standard sub lisha. ( almost done )</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>If all lines are uncheck then no update recorded&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-17 07:47:50',NULL),(13,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-01-18 00:00:00','Column date format : Add a quick way to reach calendar','','<p>From now, you have to do 2 clicks to reach calendar</p>\n<p>New feature is to reach that calendar in only 1 click.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Use right mouse click on input text area to open calendar.</p>\n<p>One click is enough</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-04 06:24:02',NULL),(14,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-01-25 00:00:00','Order all icon in psd source file with each functional name','','<p>Technical improvement to order all menu icons with a fonctional name.</p>\n<p>Here below, organization of photoshop pattern to gathering all icons in one file to increase speed.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Icon order from left to right. You will find same order position on layers list displayed in area C from top to bottom.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>There is 2 set of icon ( area A below )</p>\n<p>Top row, named <strong>Normal</strong> in picture just below on area B design normal icon looks</p>\n<p>Bottom row design shadowed looks of top row to do some hover mouse effect</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2 groups of layers gathering in area B and C just below</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_icon_order.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"976\" height=\"377\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-25 15:37:00',''),(15,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-03-10 00:00:00','Protect number of lines by page if input zero ','','<p>If user input zero in input box lines by page then system force to 1</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-10 12:20:35',NULL),(16,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-03-25 00:00:00','Javascript error if not footer page bar','<p>Add a javascript undefined test in&nbsp;<strong>lisha_cover_with_filter</strong> function</p>','<p>Test case :</p>\n<p>Choose a Lisha in update mode with&nbsp;<a href=\"../indextech.php?id=29\">__active_readonly_mode</a> = <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span></p>\n<p>Hide footer page bar with&nbsp;<a href=\"../indextech.php?id=39\">__active_bottom_bar_page</a> = <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">false</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span>Try to update a line... will generate javascript error</span></p>\n<p>This bug will stuck line update button with a javascript error</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-26 06:16:13','SRX_FOOTER_PAGE_JS_ERROR'),(17,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-03-25 00:00:00','Insert new line with date localized column made 0000-00-00','','<p>Use localization function conversion</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-26 09:42:41',NULL),(18,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-03-25 00:00:00','Unlink header page bar of main lisha and all sub lisha',NULL,NULL,'SRX',0,'2013-03-25 20:36:22',NULL),(21,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-03-26 00:00:00','Automatic generation of php user constants to javacript space','<p>Remove file constant.js into file class_lisha.php</p>\n<p>This file is automaticaly generated with php function&nbsp;<strong>get_defined_constants(true)[\'user\']</strong></p>','<p>To avoid to maintain both php and javascript constants files, we automaticaly build javascript constants from php constants space.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-26 20:25:39',NULL),(22,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-03-27 00:00:00','Add focus on column header input','','<p>You can now provide a column name to be focused</p>\n<p>See <a href=\"../indextech.php?id=64\">technical documentation</a></p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-27 06:20:08',NULL),(23,101,'General',51,'1.00','2013-03-27 00:00:00','Use standard reader and setter for column features','<p><strong>read_attribute</strong> and <strong>define_attribute</strong> standard functions had new optional input parameters&nbsp;$p_column_name</p>\n<p>Example of use <a href=\"../indextech.php?id=43\">here</a></p>','<p>Enhance of internal standard function</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-27 08:42:34',NULL),(24,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-03-27 00:00:00','create new line with value come from match code list, creation ok but value disappear in input box','<p>if calendar return value then input.filter is not setup</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>return ok but no automatic filter</p>\n<p><span>see</span></p>\n<p><span>public function </span><span>db_format(</span>$p_db_engine<span>,</span>$p_mode<span>,</span>$p_column<span>,</span>$p_value<span>)</span></p>','<p>ok</p>\n<p>bug fixe with right MySQL date format YYYY-MM-DD</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-27 21:25:36',NULL),(25,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-03-29 00:00:00','Move key column to another position then created line impossible','<p>columns size wrong !!</p>\n<p>ok, fixed</p>\n<p>Add new feature of json column called <strong>.idorigin</strong> in edit.js</p>','<p>Test case :</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/move_key_column1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"982\" height=\"163\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/move_key_column2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"990\" height=\"153\" /></p>\n<p>input values in each red input area</p>\n<p>Click on button + to create line</p>\n<p>Expected result : line creation</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Screen behaviour below:</p>\n<p>We\'ve got an error message because a mandatory column has moved</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/move_key_column3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"389\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-08 13:04:29',NULL),(26,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-03-30 00:00:00','input a value in a field that not exist in your list and change lines per page provide javascript error','<p>Fixed with tag&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>input a value in a filed that provide no result if you launch a search</p>\n<p>Then, restore your lisha</p>\n<p>input this value and do not launch search action</p>\n<p>try to change line per page value</p>\n<p>Unexpected behaviour :</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/unknown_value_change_line_by_page.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"347\" height=\"199\" /></p>\n<p>colonne size are not re compute</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Same behaviour : if you display no line with your query and try to change line per page value, it\'s a same issue.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-03-30 12:31:48','TAG_SRXFIX_CHANGE_LINE_PER_PAGE_ON_EMPTY_LIST'),(27,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-03-31 00:00:00','Add focus on error popup window [Up]','<p>Force tabindex = 10000 for ok button</p>\n<p>Default focused column see&nbsp;</p>\n<p>SRX_DEFAULT_FOCUS_COLUMN</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Change <strong>onkeydown</strong> to <strong>onkeypress</strong></p>','<p>To gain time, add focus on error popup window</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/focus_on_error_popup.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"401\" height=\"170\" /></p>\n<p>Enable Enter key pressed to close directly this popup and return to default column focused if any</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-26 05:32:28','SRX_ADD_ONKEYDOWN_EVENT'),(28,100,'update',51,'1.00','2013-04-01 00:00:00','Add date format control !','<p>Please use date format of database engine translation</p>','<p>Add date format control if user input a wrong format to create or modify a date</p>','SRX',5,'2013-09-13 06:15:12',NULL),(29,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-04-01 00:00:00','Tab key on input area doesn\'t scroll list body !','','<p>To see that, have a list larger than your screen with at least one row</p>\n<p>Then try to jump to last right input area using tab key</p>','SRX',5,'2013-09-13 08:11:59',NULL),(30,101,'update',50,'1.00','2013-04-01 00:00:00','Create or update failed if you use name [b]index[/b] of a column name in table','<p>ok</p>','<p>Probably a missing protection of column name by ``</p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-03 12:45:48',NULL),(31,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-04-03 00:00:00','Return of match code in non focused input does\'nt keep focus','<p>This function doesn\'t run by browser</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p>// Javascript focus call</p>\n<p>// FOCUS ISSUE ON MATCHCODE THIS CODE DOESN\'T RUN BY BROWSER</p>\n<p>//==================================================================</p>\n<p><span>if</span>(<span>isset</span>(<span>$this</span>-&gt;c_default_input_focus_id))</p>\n<p>{</p>\n<p><span>$tmp </span>= <span>\"th_input_\"</span>.<span>$this</span>-&gt;c_default_input_focus_id.<span>\"__\"</span>.<span>$this</span>-&gt;c_id;</p>\n<p><span>$lisha </span><span>.= </span>\'&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;</p>\n<p>function lisha_focus_timer\'<span>.</span><span>$this</span><span>-&gt;c_id.</span>\'()</p>\n<p>{</p>\n<p>try</p>\n<p>{</p>\n<p>document.getElementById(\"\'<span>.</span><span>$tmp</span><span>.</span>\'\").focus();</p>\n<p>clearInterval(myVar\'<span>.</span><span>$this</span><span>-&gt;c_id.</span>\');</p>\n<p>}</p>\n<p>catch (e)</p>\n<p>{</p>\n<p>}</p>\n<p>}</p>\n<p>var myVar\'<span>.</span><span>$this</span><span>-&gt;c_id.</span>\'=setInterval(function(){lisha_focus_timer\'<span>.</span><span>$this</span><span>-&gt;c_id.</span>\'()},1000);</p>\n<p>lisha_focus_timer\'<span>.</span><span>$this</span><span>-&gt;c_id.</span>\'();</p>\n<p>&lt;/script&gt;</p>\n<p>\'<span>;</span></p>\n<p>}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','SRX',4,'2013-05-13 04:38:06',NULL),(32,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-04-03 00:00:00','Match code lisha have default focus','<p>Technical way to add focus on a column</p>\n<p>$my_obj-&gt;define_column_lov(\'ord\',\'<strong>Order</strong>\',__TEXT__,__WRAP__,__LEFT__,__PERCENT__,__DISPLAY__<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>,true</strong></span>);</p>','<p>Example below just after left click on Class match code to call extra list</p>\n<p>We see that Order column input area get directly the focus</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/define_default_focus_on_matchcode.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"519\" height=\"380\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-03 15:28:54',NULL),(33,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-04-03 00:00:00','Add font size features on line color group',NULL,NULL,'SRX',2,'2013-04-06 08:25:21',NULL),(34,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-04-03 00:00:00','Do the excel export','<p>Issue :</p>\n<p>I can\'t manage a progress bar because :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Writing information session using&nbsp;session_write_close() will force a new MySQL connexion each time</li>\n<li>Standard output will write information using&nbsp;<strong>header</strong>(\"Content-type: application/csv; charset=utf-8\");</li>\n</ul>','<p>Active excel button below :</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/Active_excel_export.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"126\" height=\"62\" /></p>\n<p>means :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Export only rows after filter if any</li>\n<li>Export only checked line if any else export all filtering rows</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/export_confirmation.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"398\" height=\"172\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Final popup message</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/export_final_popup.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"398\" height=\"168\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-29 06:07:45',NULL),(35,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-04-04 00:00:00','Do direct cells update on body rows','<p>Keep scrollTop position of lift</p>','<p>You can now update data directly into list except for forbidden column of course</p>\n<p>Just double click to get in iupdate mode.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/cell_update.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"828\" height=\"209\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-13 04:29:48',NULL),(36,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-04-04 00:00:00','Add watermark on forbidden column to have visual limitation effect','','<p>At a glance with less&nbsp;opacity on fordibben column</p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-06 08:24:31',NULL),(37,100,'Documentation',51,'1.00','2013-04-06 00:00:00','Do a lisha configuration checklist !','','<p>Check list :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">You can\'t add __FORBIDDEN__ attribute to a hidden column</span> : It\'s not a right restriction --&gt; Internal bug fixed</li>\n</ul>','SRX',5,'2013-09-13 08:11:50',NULL),(38,100,'Documentation',51,'1.00','2013-04-06 00:00:00','Do a lisha wizard !','','<p>Do an utility to help someone to build a new lisha configuration.</p>\n<p>This we raise warning and errors detected but will not write configuration file.</p>','SRX',5,'2013-09-13 08:12:05',NULL),(39,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-04-08 00:00:00','You can\'t add __FORBIDDEN__ attribute to a hidden column','<p>Fixed</p>','<p>It\'s a bug.</p>\n<p>We can hide or show any column available in original column defined by lisha builder.</p>\n<p>So anyone can have additional check feature control <strong>__FORBIDDEN__</strong>.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-07 13:00:44',NULL),(40,100,'update',51,'1.00','2013-04-09 00:00:00','Hide column contextual marble on forbidden feature or special color column','','<p>Here below example on updating mode</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/update_remove_contextmenu_marble.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>We remove marble on forbidden columns and reserved <a href=\"../indextech.php?id=103\" target=\"_blank\">column for set of color</a></p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-09 08:32:07',NULL),(41,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-04-09 00:00:00','Search on (\\) antislash digit doesn\'t work !','<p>seems to be a MySL issue on UTF-8 format</p>\n<p>have look to <a href=\"http://bugs.mysql.com/bug.php?id=68901\" target=\"_blank\">that</a></p>\n<p>Stand by</p>','','SRX',3,'2013-08-11 06:51:43',NULL),(42,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-04-11 00:00:00','Edition buttons doesn\'t hide after reset filter','','<p>On update lisha mode</p>\n<p>Select at least 1 row for update</p>\n<p>So, update button are ungrey</p>\n<p>Then do a reset filter</p>\n<p>Bug : Edit button are still in available mode</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><object width=\"765\" height=\"340\" data=\"../doc_tech/video/bug_after_reset_filter.mov\" type=\"video/quicktime\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"../doc_tech/video/bug_after_reset_filter.mov\" /></object></p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-11 14:53:40','SRX_fix_update_buttons_display_mode'),(43,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-04-12 00:00:00','Editing rows on second page doesn\'t display selected line','<p>force limit to 0,xxxx</p>','<p>Seems wrong page number</p>\n<p>Have to reset to page 1</p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-12 08:01:06','SRX_fix_edit_row_on_not_first_page'),(44,100,'update',51,'1.00','2013-04-12 00:00:00','Hide navigation bar page when editing rows','','<p>Hide navigation page because page navigation doesn\'t manage when we are editing lines&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-04-12 08:03:02',NULL),(45,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-05-06 00:00:00','Automatic size of page input index to display depend on max page number','','<p>Remove hard coded value = 1</p>\n<p>if you have a large number enable for your index page then input box will be larger.</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_inpiut_index_page_size.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"592\" height=\"270\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-06 13:37:08',NULL),(46,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-05-06 00:00:00','Add new column data type : checkbox','<p>Simple click on displayed item will jump into cell update mode</p>\n<p>if no data displayed in cell then just click on cell to jump on update mode</p>','<p>Add new column type : checkbox</p>\n<p>Enable you to draw a checkbox in column to display two stats of value ( true or false )</p>\n<p>Example below</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/checkbox_example.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"19\" height=\"140\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-13 08:25:32',NULL),(47,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-05-07 00:00:00','javascript error on sub lisha reset button','<p>Add additional test condition on reduce toolbar</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/sublisha_clean_button_error.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"805\" height=\"91\" /></p>','<p>reset filter button raise js error</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/error_js_on_reset_button.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"315\" height=\"240\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-08 03:54:44',NULL),(48,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-05-07 00:00:00','Add a missing MySQL `` protection','<p>Technical function to use <strong>get_quote_col</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/add_mysql_field_protection.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"630\" height=\"91\" /></p>','<p>on a field called index, trying to display list of available values raise MySQL error cause missing field protection</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-07 08:21:54',NULL),(49,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-05-10 00:00:00','Wrong lisha left lift position when call sublisha of possible values on column','<p>Seems to be a browser bug and fixe</p>','<p>You can see issue when you have a larger lisha than your screen and you move horizontal lift on the right.</p>\n<p>Then, call with right click list of values on a column</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Bug : Main lisha offset lift display a reset position of your horizontal lift.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_sublisha_wrong_left_position.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"562\" height=\"442\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-10 05:29:20','SRX_fixe_lift_offset_position'),(50,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-05-10 00:00:00','Export list is asynchronous with displayed body','','<p>If you input a filter without refresh your lisha content</p>\n<p>then click on export button</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>So export will apply filter and there is unmatched result between export content and result displayed in your lisha body screen.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_export_asynchronous_body_content.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"457\" height=\"286\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Suggestion : Force a refresh of lisha body just on export button click</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Add new message that informe user there is no line to export</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_export_no_line.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"408\" height=\"178\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-10 08:50:43',NULL),(76,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-08-11 00:00:00','Performance : Remove condition in derived table','<p>To do</p>\n<p>Have to remove&nbsp;<strong>define_fast_field</strong> stuff</p>','<p>Today, we have an encapsulation of all queries to do looks transformation like that following</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span> DATE_FORMAT(`daterec`,\'%d/%m/%Y\') <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `daterec`,`description` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `description`,`mode` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `mode`,`text` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `text`,`amount` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `amount`,`encrypt` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `encrypt`,`index` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `index`,`checkme` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `checkme`,`status` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `status`,DATE_FORMAT(`datum`,\'%d/%m/%Y\') <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `datum`,`MyGroupTheme` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `MyGroupTheme`,CONCAT(\'\',`index`) <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `lisha_internal_key_concat`</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">FROM</span> (</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><em><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span></em><br /><em> `transaction`.`index` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `index`,</em><br /><em> `transaction`.`daterec` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `daterec`,</em><br /><em> `transaction`.`description` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `description`,</em><br /><em> `transaction`.`amount` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `amount`,</em><br /><em> IF(MOD(`transaction`.`index`,2)=0,MD5(`transaction`.`amount`),SHA1(`transaction`.`amount`)) <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `encrypt`,</em><br /><em> CONCAT(\'[b]\',`transaction`.`status`,\'[/b]\') <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `status`,</em><br /><em> `transaction`.`checkme` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `checkme`,</em><br /><em> `transaction`.`datum` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `datum`,</em><br /><em> `transaction`.`mode` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `mode`,</em><br /><em> `TRAN2`.`text` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `text`,</em><br /><em> `transaction`.`status` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> `MyGroupTheme`</em><br /><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><em> FROM</em></span><br /><em> `transaction`, -- No alias on update table !!</em><br /><em> `transaction2` `TRAN2`</em><br /><em> WHERE 1 = 1</em><br /><em> AND `transaction`.`mode` = `TRAN2`.`mode`</em><br /><em> )</em> deriv</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">WHERE</span> 1 = 1</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">ORDER BY</span> deriv.`daterec` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">ASC</span> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">LIMIT</span> 8000,40</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Try to reach that kind of query</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span></p>\n<p>`transaction`.`index` AS `index`,<br /> <span style=\"color: #008000;\">DATE_FORMAT(</span><span style=\"color: #808080;\">`transaction`.`daterec`</span><span style=\"color: #008000;\">,\'%d/%m/%Y\')</span> AS `daterec`,<br /> `transaction`.`description` AS `description`,<br /> `transaction`.`amount` AS `amount`,<br /> IF(MOD(`transaction`.`index`,2)=0,MD5(`transaction`.`amount`),SHA1(`transaction`.`amount`)) AS `encrypt`,<br /> CONCAT(\'[b]\',`transaction`.`status`,\'[/b]\') AS `status`,<br /> `transaction`.`checkme` AS `checkme`,<br /> `transaction`.`datum` AS `datum`,<br /> `transaction`.`mode` AS `mode`,<br /> `TRAN2`.`text` AS `text`,<br /> `transaction`.`status` AS `MyGroupTheme`<br /> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">FROM</span><br /> `transaction`, -- No alias on update table !!<br /> `transaction2` `TRAN2`<br /> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">WHERE</span> 1 = 1<br /> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AND</span> `transaction`.`mode` = `TRAN2`.`mode`<br /> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">ORDER BY</span> `daterec` <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">ASC LIMIT</span> 1300,40</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Todo :</span></strong></p>\n<p>You have to define <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">alias name for each column</span></p>\n<p>AND</p>\n<p>a full part of <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>before alias</strong></span> name part to do localization transormation</p>\n<p>eg of following column named <strong><em>mynom</em></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span><em>(</em></span></strong><br /><strong><span><em>SELECT&nbsp;</em></span></strong><br /><strong><span><em>CASE IFNULL(length(`DEFAUT`),0)+IFNULL(length(`NEUTRE`),0)&nbsp;</em></span></strong><br /><strong><span><em>WHEN 0</em></span></strong><br /><strong><span><em>THEN (CONCAT(\'[b][color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color][/b]\'))&nbsp;</em></span></strong><br /><strong><span><em>ELSE (CONCAT(\'[color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color]\'))</em></span></strong><br /><strong><span><em>END</em></span></strong><br /><span><em><strong>)</strong></em></span></p>\n<p>because, that kind of query wokrs</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: xx-small; color: #0000ff;\"><em>SELECT</em></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> (</em></span></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> SELECT </em></span></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> CASE IFNULL(length(`DEFAUT`),0)+IFNULL(length(`NEUTRE`),0) </em></span></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> WHEN 0</em></span></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> THEN (CONCAT(\'[b][color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color][/b]\')) </em></span></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> ELSE (CONCAT(\'[color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color]\'))</em></span></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> END</em></span></strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong> )</strong></span> <strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> \'mynom\'</strong>,</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `DESCRIPTION` AS \'DESCRIPTION\', </em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `ID` AS \'ID\',</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `Version` AS \'Version\',</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `TYPE` AS \'TYPE\',</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `DEFAUT` AS \'DEFAUT\', </em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `NEUTRE` AS \'NEUTRE\', </em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `COMMENTAIRE` AS \'COMMENTAIRE\',</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> (</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> SELECT</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> CASE IFNULL(length(`DEFAUT`),0)+IFNULL(length(`NEUTRE`),0) </em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> WHEN 0</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> THEN \'[img]images/obligatoire.png[/img]\' </em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> ELSE \'\' </em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> END</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> ) AS \'obligatoire\',</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `IDP` AS \'IDP\'</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> FROM</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> `ikn_icode_parameter` </em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> WHERE 1 = 1</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> AND `ID` = 50</em></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em> AND `TYPE` = \'IN\'</em></span><br /><em><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AND</span> <span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>(</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>SELECT&nbsp;</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>CASE&nbsp;IFNULL(length(`DEFAUT`),0)+IFNULL(length(`NEUTRE`),0)&nbsp;</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>WHEN 0</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>THEN (CONCAT(\'[b][color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color][/b]\'))&nbsp;</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>ELSE (CONCAT(\'[color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color]\'))</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>END</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><em><strong>)</strong></em></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">LIKE</span> \'%Depot%\'</em><br /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><em><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"> ORDER BY</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>(</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>SELECT&nbsp;</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>CASE&nbsp;IFNULL(length(`DEFAUT`),0)+IFNULL(length(`NEUTRE`),0)&nbsp;</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>WHEN 0</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>THEN (CONCAT(\'[b][color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color][/b]\'))&nbsp;</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>ELSE (CONCAT(\'[color=#FF0000]\',`nom`,\'[/color]\'))</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><strong><em>END</em></strong></span><br /><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><em><strong>)</strong></em></span>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">DESC</span></em></span></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Special case of <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">UNION</span> or <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">UNION ALL</span> :</p>\n<p>if you have to use</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span> 1 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span>&nbsp;`A`</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">UNION</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span> 2 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span>&nbsp;`A`</p>\n<p>Please, have to encapsulate manualy you original query in that form</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>$query = \'<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span>&nbsp;<strong>`main`.`A`</strong> <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span> <strong>`F1`</strong></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">FROM</span> (<br /><em><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span> 1 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span>&nbsp;`A`</em></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><em>UNION</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><em><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">SELECT</span> 2 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">AS</span>&nbsp;`A`</em><br />) `main`\';</p>\n<p><strong>$my_object</strong><span>-&gt;<span>define_attribute</span>(</span><span>\'</span><span>__main_query</span><span>\'</span><span>,&nbsp;</span><span>$query</span><span>);</span></p>\n<p>In this query above, your column description will be</p>\n<p><strong>$my_object</strong><span>-&gt;</span><span>define_column</span><span>(\'<span style=\"color: #800000;\">`main`.`A`</span>\'</span><em><span>,</span></em>\'<span style=\"color: #800000;\">`F1`</span>\'<span>,\'<span style=\"color: #800000;\">My_column_name</span>\'</span><span>,</span><span><span class=\"jump\">__TEXT__</span>,&nbsp;</span><span><span class=\"jump\">__WRAP__</span></span><span>,&nbsp;</span><span><span class=\"jump\">__CENTER__</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"jump\">__EXACT__</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"jump\">__DISPLAY__</span></span><span>);</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-03 06:12:40',NULL),(51,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-05-14 00:00:00','header row doesn\'t scrawl on a large content of sub lisha','<p>Seems to be bug browser</p>\n<p>Force reload of sub lisha</p>\n<p>Fix with <strong>lisha_reset</strong> call :</p>\n<p>// Browser bug, force refresh sub lisha</p>\n<p>lisha_reset<span>(</span><span>lisha_id</span><span>+</span><span>\'_child\'</span><span>)</span><span>;</span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>In sublisha, only body scrowl</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_sublisha_lift_position.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"517\" height=\"352\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-14 09:36:29',NULL),(52,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-05-15 00:00:00','Remove add button from sublisha load filter','<p>Ok, button add removed in this sub lisha</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_remove_add_button_filter_liste.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"557\" height=\"389\" /></p>','<p>You can\'t add a new line in filter list.</p>\n<p>You can update filter name or / and remove it.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-15 13:44:32',NULL),(53,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-05-17 00:00:00','Red marble disapears if clear all filter','<p>Fixed.</p>\n<p>Missing some initial record into&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">$this</span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #888888;\">c_columns_init</span> structure</p>\n<p>Eg:</p>\n<p>// Keep initial value in memory</p>\n<p><span>$this</span>-&gt;c_columns_init[<span>$column_id</span>][<span>\'lov\'</span>][<span>\'sql\'</span>] = <span>$p_sql</span>;</p>\n<p><span>$this</span>-&gt;c_columns_init[<span>$column_id</span>][<span>\'lov\'</span>][<span>\'title\'</span>] = <span>$p_title</span>;</p>\n<p><span>$this</span>-&gt;c_columns_init[<span>$column_id</span>][<span>\'lov\'</span>][<span>\'col_return\'</span>] = <span>$p_col_return</span>;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>if you have some matched list defined and you clear all filter to restore initials values then some information disapear.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-23 13:45:18',NULL),(54,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-05-20 00:00:00','Can\'t define specified row color theme for sub lisha','<p>Limitation come from function <strong>generate_color_line_style()</strong> that is refered to&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">$this</span>-&gt;<span style=\"color: #808080;\">c_color_mask</span> array.</p>','<p>Current limitation :</p>\n<p>All sub lisha color line theme use default color 0 of main lisha</p>\n<p>You can\'t add specified theme color for sub lisha using&nbsp;<strong>define_line_theme</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SRX',0,'2013-09-13 06:15:26',NULL),(55,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-05-20 00:00:00','define_column_lov_order needs only 2 parameters','','<p>Original function&nbsp;<strong>define_column_lov_order</strong> needs 3 parameters.</p>\n<p>We remove priority by automatic priority level defined by order of&nbsp;<strong>define_column_lov_order</strong> call.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>First call define the highest priority and then priority decrease</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-20 14:18:15',NULL),(56,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-05-21 00:00:00','Hide default focus column will rise js error when trying to update a row','<p>Exclude default column focus from list of column to show/hide</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_do_not_display_hide_in_focus_column_list.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"534\" height=\"370\" /></p>\n<p>and from contextual menu of column</p>\n<p>Eg below datum is default focus column</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_do_not_display_hide_in_focus_column.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"274\" height=\"295\" /></p>','<p>Js error when you hide column define as default column focus</p>\n<p>if a default column focus is defined then you have to exclude this one from column show/hide list</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-22 11:59:42',NULL),(57,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-05-23 00:00:00','Add dynamic control on column list display and hide feature','','<p>Add 2 additionnal check on display / hide column feature</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Can\'t hide focus column</li>\n<li>Have at least one column displayed</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If error occurs then remove ok button in bottom right corner</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_column_list_check_display.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"346\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-23 09:31:14',NULL),(58,100,'update',51,'1.00','2013-05-23 00:00:00','Add column control type __LISTED__ feature','','<p>When we define column control type to&nbsp;__LISTED__ that means ::</p>\n<ul>\n<li>We have to defined LOV</li>\n<li>Only entries return by this LOV is granted to update value of column</li>\n</ul>','SRX',5,'2013-09-15 05:58:50',NULL),(59,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-05-23 00:00:00','Add search mode feature to general list column','','<p>here</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_add_all_search_mode_columns.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"537\" height=\"387\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-23 15:14:25',NULL),(60,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-05-25 00:00:00','Json delete missing when unselected line rise javascript error','<p>Fixe :</p>\n<p>Replace</p>\n<p>eval(\'lisha.\'+id+\'.selected_line.L\'+line+\'.selected = false;\');</p>\n<p>by</p>\n<p><span>eval</span><span>(</span>\'<strong>delete</strong> lisha.\'<span>+</span><span>id</span><span>+</span>\'.selected_line.L\'<span>+</span><span>line</span><span>+</span>\';\'<span>)</span><span>;</span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>','<p>Test case in update mode :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Selected a line</li>\n<li>Do a cell value update</li>\n<li>record modification by pressing enter</li>\n<li>Try to unselect line</li>\n</ol>\n<p>A javascript error rise</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_json_selected_line_error.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"179\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-25 08:49:14',NULL),(61,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-05-25 00:00:00','No data input check on filed if update a row !!','<p>Done</p>\n<p>Group data check in private function called&nbsp;<strong>update_data_check</strong>($tab_val_col)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>When you select a row and remove value from mandatory one, &nbsp;no error message</p>\n<p>Too bad</p>\n<p>Fixe it please !!</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-25 19:21:02',NULL),(62,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-05-26 00:00:00','Performance : Internal sql builder : replace derived table by direct sql action','<p>Keep deriv table to formating fields but move where condition in original query to exclude as soon as possible rows from result</p>\n<p>Have to define alias for table and fields to avoid ambiguous name</p>\n<p>See <a href=\"../indextech.php?id=113\" target=\"_blank\">rules</a> documentation for furthers information about main query formating requirement.</p>','<p>Today, lisha build final query using derived table</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #888888;\">EXPLAIN SELECT DATE_FORMAT(`daterec` ,\'%d/%m/%Y\') AS `daterec`,`description` AS `description`,`mode` AS `mode`,`ModuleLib` AS `ModuleLib`,`amount` AS `amount`,`upper` AS `upper`,`index` AS `index`,`checkme` AS `checkme`,`status` AS `status`,DATE_FORMAT(`datum` ,\'%Y-%m-%d\') AS `datum`,`MyGroupTheme` AS `MyGroupTheme`,CONCAT(\'\',`index`) AS `lisha_internal_key_concat` FROM (</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> SELECT</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`index` AS `index`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`daterec` AS `daterec`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`description` AS `description`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`amount` AS `amount`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> UPPER(`TRAN`.`amount`) AS `upper`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`status` AS `status`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`checkme` AS `checkme`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`datum` AS `datum`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`mode` AS `mode`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN2`.`text` AS `ModuleLib`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `TRAN`.`status` AS `MyGroupTheme`</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> FROM </span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `transaction` `TRAN`,</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> `transaction2` `TRAN2`</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> WHERE 1 = 1</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> AND `TRAN`.`mode` = `TRAN2`.`mode`</span><br /><span style=\"color: #888888;\"> ) deriv WHERE 1 = 1 ORDER BY `index` DESC,`description` DESC,`amount` ASC LIMIT 0,70;</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Target :</p>\n<p>Remove derived table because of poor\'s performance acces in database.</p>\n<p>Derived table force full scan table</p>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Warning :&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p>This feature increase performance but you lost all MySQL transformation in your query</p>\n<p>You have to do a choice.</p>\n<p>Back to deriv format for full fonctionnal MySQL operation supported</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SRX',4,'2013-06-05 04:27:37',NULL),(63,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-05-31 00:00:00','On save_lines javascript function, add methode on_update, after','','<p>Fixe issue that no check done in column list sub lisha if focus column is hidden</p>','SRX',2,'2013-05-31 20:04:44',NULL),(64,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-06-01 00:00:00','Checkbox column type : Forbidden cell update if currently on update mode','','<p>When you are updating a set of rows then cell update function have to be unavailable to avoid mistake</p>\n<p>That rule had to be include for checkbox column type.</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_disable_checkbox_in_update_mode.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"171\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-06-02 04:41:47',NULL),(65,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-06-04 00:00:00','Add thousand separator using localization in navigation tool bar','<p>Ok, done</p>\n<p>Have to enhance number to display using localization information</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/row_count_add_thousand_separator.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"743\" height=\"47\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Use function&nbsp;<strong>number_format</strong>($this-&gt;c_recordset_line,0,\'\', \' \')</p>','<p>Add thousand separator in navigation toolbar</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-29 06:25:16',NULL),(67,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-06-04 00:00:00','Performance : Add parameters to enable/disable auto quick search on column','<p>Ok</p>\n<p>Standard parameters name :&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #008080;\">__active_quick_search</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>by default set to&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">true</span>&nbsp;( active )</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>When you start to type something in head column input area then a quick search is send to server to retourne some lines matched.</p>\n<p>This fonction may be very long to provide response on a non key column on huge table.</p>\n<p>To avoid that, please add new parameters to enable or disable this fonction ( default : enable )</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_active_quick_search.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"185\" height=\"205\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-06-06 10:32:46',NULL),(68,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-06-05 00:00:00','Latence after pressing enter on input box search',NULL,NULL,'SRX',2,'2013-06-05 08:54:57',NULL),(69,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-06-06 00:00:00','Lisha without any navigation bar','<ul>\n<li>Don\'t compute total of rows ( Performance enhancement )</li>\n<li>check wait div size</li>\n</ul>','<p>Check lisha behaviour if no navigation bar</p>\n<p>Remove request to have total of rows after filtering or refreshing action</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-29 06:28:20',NULL),(70,100,'update',51,'1.00','2013-07-02 00:00:00','Performance : Update rows are plug directly on update table','<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_key_closer_core.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"971\" height=\"119\" /></p>','<p>Technical enhancement to have fast response time</p>','SRX',2,'2013-07-02 08:23:22',NULL),(71,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-07-05 00:00:00','Remove hard coded background color','<p>Ugly fix&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We compute a background color into dynamic css background style</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/SRX_hard_coded_bgcolor.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"413\" height=\"334\" /></p>','<p>Internal enhancement</p>\n<p>Each theme has his own background color</p>','SRX',2,'2013-07-05 13:20:52',NULL),(72,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-07-05 00:00:00','A customer filter setup in url, main raz don\'t keep filter condition','<p>Fixed</p>\n<p>Add new public variable called $filter_name</p>\n<p>This one contains customer filter to reload after pushing main reset button.</p>','<p>Using following url</p>\n<p>http://lisha.dtravel/zdev/?f1=test</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Then, press reset filter button will erase everything</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Expected result : Keep filter option forced by url key filter <strong>f1=test</strong></p>','SRX',2,'2013-07-11 13:20:38',NULL),(73,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-07-10 00:00:00','Wrong page number after add a new row. Please force page 1','<p>Fixed</p>\n<p>Force return to page 1 after a successfull record using</p>\n<p>$this-&gt;define_attribute(\'__current_page\',1);<br /> $this-&gt;define_limit_min(0);</p>','<p>Sequence :</p>\n<p>Have a lisha in update mode to add a new line</p>\n<p>Move to page number 2</p>\n<p>Add a new line with all require fields</p>\n<p>Lisha refresh screen without at least your last record because current page number is still on page 2 !!</p>\n<p>Fix require to force page number to one after a sucessfull record</p>','SRX',2,'2013-07-15 12:05:06',NULL),(74,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-07-23 00:00:00','Input value not keep in input header if come from match code','<p>Fixed in <strong>lisha_child.js</strong> using the following</p>\n<p>// Keep search filter options in column input header<br /> <span style=\"color: #888888;\">lisha_define_filter(parent,encodeURIComponent(document.getElementById(\'th_input_\'+parent_column+\'__\'+parent).value),parent_column,false);</span></p>','<p>You need a lisha with a focus column to do this test.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-07-23 11:01:29',NULL),(75,100,'Documentation',51,'1.00','2013-07-27 00:00:00','Add shortcut keyboard quick page help CTRL+F11 ( to continue )','','<p>Mouve mouse hover an icon and then press CTRL+F11 to call related help page!</p>','SRX',3,'2013-09-21 13:27:28',NULL),(77,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-08-18 00:00:00','Do a quick search on column and erase input content will keep in memory','<p>Add new capture event <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">onkeydown</span>&nbsp;in column input box</p>\n<p>function <strong>lisha_input_keydown_pressed</strong>&nbsp;for all special key pressed that provide no digit ( Del, suppr, escape, function key f1...F12.. and so on )</p>\n<p>This new function is defined in&nbsp;<strong>js/input_col.js</strong> file</p>','<p>Sequence :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Type something no exist in column A</li>\n<li>Erase content of input box in column A</li>\n<li>Go to column B</li>\n<li>Type one digit exist in column B</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Result : No result</strong></span></p>\n<p>Expected result : Found something</p>\n<p>Explanation : First entry input in column A is still here despite of deletion.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-18 20:01:15',NULL),(78,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-08-26 00:00:00','Export of 100 000 rows cause none answer','<p>change time out of&nbsp;function export_list</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Rise to 20 seconds one time.</p>\n<p>conf[\'delai_tentative\'] = 20000;<br /> conf[\'max_tentative\'] = 2;</p>','<p>No popup apperas with amouth of rows and confirmation message</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-27 06:19:35',NULL),(79,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-08-27 00:00:00','Compress export list','','<p>Seems more difficult than expected</p>','SRX',4,'2013-09-13 08:12:26',NULL),(80,100,'update',51,'1.00','2013-08-28 00:00:00','Update row mode only : Do not reset page number position !','<p>We have to restore page 1 on updating mode</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We can keep in memory current page to restore that when exit update mode.</p>\n<p>Two values to record</p>\n<p>$this-&gt;define_attribute(\'__current_page\',1); (&nbsp;c_active_page )<br />$this-&gt;define_limit_min(0);</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Build 2 new functions</p>\n<p>$this-&gt;clear_page_position_recorded();</p>\n<p>$this-&gt;restore_page_position();</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>Currently, when we do a rows update then after validation, we have a page reset position to 1.</p>\n<p>Expected : To stay on the same page position</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Caution</strong></span> : If user use Add or Delete button then reset to page position 1.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-29 09:32:55',NULL),(81,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-08-28 00:00:00','Export button not available after a row update','','<p>Do some update row</p>\n<p>Record your row</p>\n<p>Then, in toolbar, export button stay greyed</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-28 06:29:21',NULL),(82,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-08-29 00:00:00','Multi row update : Return key pressed check default column','<p>Ok, done</p>\n<p>See file class_graphic.php</p>\n<p>Update event onkeypressed</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/onkey_pressed_exit_return_to_check.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"843\" height=\"83\" /></p>','<p>Test case :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Choose more than one row with different values in default column ( column which get focus by default after any action )</li>\n<li>Go to update mode</li>\n<li>As expected, your cursor will be in default column</li>\n<li>Then press straight ENTER</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Defect : Your column check box will be set</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/checkbox_update_on_return.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"123\" height=\"93\" /></p>\n<p>Expected result : Do not check the update box then ENTER</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-29 06:24:03',NULL),(83,100,'update',50,'1.00','2013-08-29 00:00:00','Remove column sort option in row update mode','<p>Remove contextual menu from column header ( left click only is removed, right click is still available )</p>','<p>You have to limit column action in updating mode</p>\n<p>Good practice will to setup your column configuration looks before to update.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-02 16:00:00',NULL),(84,100,'update',51,'1.00','2013-08-29 00:00:00','Remove column option menu in updating mode','','<p>When you are currently updating rows ( no cell update ), we have to remove column options like sort, alignment, hidding and so on..</p>\n<p>Main concept is you first change main lisha looks using column option and then you can do update.</p>','SRX',2,'2013-08-29 09:37:09',NULL),(85,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-09-02 00:00:00','Increase number of row by page then try to check last row in list','<p>Fixed</p>\n<p>Optimized with only one Ajax call to do the job</p>','<p>Test case :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Add 1 row by page in navigation page bar</li>\n<li>Try to check last row in the list ( which one is new )</li>\n</ol><hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Result : Javascript error</p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Expected : Checked bow without any error</p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-03 06:10:17',NULL),(86,100,'General',50,'1.00','2013-09-04 00:00:00','Fix Group by condition','<p>No great way to fixe it</p>\n<p>Have to encapsulated your query to solve problem.</p>\n<p><a href=\"../indextech.php?id=128\" target=\"_blank\">See</a></p>','<p>$_SESSION[$this-&gt;c_ssid][\'lisha\'][\'configuration\'][10]</p>\n<p>add</p>\n<p>$_SESSION[$this-&gt;c_ssid][\'lisha\'][\'configuration\'][11]</p>\n<p><strong>No way to solve it properly.</strong></p>','SRX',4,'2013-09-10 15:03:14',NULL),(87,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-09-05 00:00:00','Change number of rows by page, grey style doesn\'t on screen ',NULL,NULL,'SRX',2,'2013-09-21 13:23:01',NULL),(88,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-09-05 00:00:00','Force grey color on load filter button if no customer filter recorder','','<p>Not yet over</p>\n<p>Issue to fixe</p>\n<p>Have to figure out how refresh <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">only</span> toolbar when return on popup windows</p>','SRX',3,'2013-09-15 06:05:33',NULL),(89,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-09-09 00:00:00','Sub window position if main div not in absolute position','<p>use the following javascript function</p>\n<p><strong>internal_sub_lisha_toolbar_top_position</strong></p>\n<p>Caution of specific internal lisha for distinct values.</p>','<p>If your div is not set in absolute position, top position of internal sub lisha is wrong</p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-09 09:26:15',NULL),(90,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-09-10 00:00:00','Date column quick search format is wrong','','<p>Seems to be ok</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/date_fit_localization_on_fast_search.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"215\" height=\"338\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-10 14:07:20',NULL),(91,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-09-10 00:00:00','Date column search on date with [b]hours[/b] format doesn\'t work well','','<p>Try to search something on datetime format column</p>\n<p>Exact search doesn\'t work</p>\n<p>Caution : Date format is not equal with date time format</p>','SRX',5,'2013-09-21 13:21:16',NULL),(92,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-09-11 00:00:00','Add limit of rows to export','<p>Add new main configuration paremeters ( index = 11 )</p>\n<p>That value set up max limit of rows export.</p>\n<p>A high value will request a quiet huge of disk space to do export.</p>\n<p>Example :</p>\n<p>Exporting 700 000 lines that build a 140 Mo csv file will require a temporary free space disk about 1.3 Gb</p>\n<p>Add extra popup information then limit reached</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/message_of_export_limit.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"403\" height=\"174\" /></p>','<p>If i try to export up to 700 000 rows then 1 Go free disk is required</p>\n<p>and if no space free disk available, we get this error</p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/out_of%20_free_disk_memory.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"592\" height=\"606\" /></p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-11 11:32:39',NULL),(93,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-09-12 00:00:00','Add column type DATETIME','','<p>Manage localization format on date time field.</p>\n<p>Use new type of data that manage following template :&nbsp;2013-09-12 08:31:41</p>','SRX',0,'2013-09-13 06:14:37',NULL),(94,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-09-13 00:00:00','Add advanced filter options on columns','','<p>Add new window under menu <strong>Advanced filter</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"screenshot/advanced_filter_menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"170\" height=\"63\" /></p>\n<p>Features :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>First tab with a lisha to list all <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">values</span> to <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">include</span> in query</li>\n<li>Second tab with a lisha to list all <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">values</span> to <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">exclude</span> in query</li>\n<li>third tab with a lisha to list all <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">range</span> values to <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">include</span></li>\n<li>fourth&nbsp;tab with a lisha to list all <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">range</span> values to <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">exlude</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>Exclusion had a higher priority on inclusion</p>\n<p>SELECT * &nbsp;FROM `transaction` WHERE `index` in (200200) and `index` not in (200200)</p>\n<p>will return no row</p>','SRX',5,'2013-09-13 08:29:48',NULL),(95,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-09-14 00:00:00','Uncheck line checkbox not recorded','<p><strong>Tips :</strong></p>\n<p>Don\'t delete unselect line entrie. Transfert value false or true to feature .selected.</p>\n<p>Replace</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">eval(\'delete lisha.\'+id+\'.selected_line.L\'+i+\';\');</span></p>\n<p>by</p>\n<p>eval(\'lisha.\'+id+\'.selected_line.L\'+i+\'.selected = false;\');<br /><br /></p>','<p>Test case :</p>\n<ol>\n<li>On first page, checkbox first line</li>\n<li>Then uncheck the box</li>\n<li>go to page 2</li>\n<li>Back to page 1</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Result : Line is still checked</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Expected result : Line unchecked.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-14 20:03:58','SRX_UNCHECKBOX_JSON_FEATURE'),(96,100,'display',50,'1.00','2013-09-15 00:00:00','Sort on column doesn\'t work if try to move a column then abort','<p>Something missing in if... else part</p>\n<p>Add new line below to reset global javascript variable properly for destination column id</p>\n<p>eval(\'lisha.\'+lisha_id_move+\'.destination_column = undefined;\');</p>','<p>Test case:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Start to move a column position but stay on original position ( icon of move have a forbidden look )</li>\n<li>release mouse button</li>\n<li>Try to sort a column</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Result : No sort order proceed</p>\n<p>Expected result : Sort proceed has requested</p>','SRX',2,'2013-09-21 13:19:53','SRX_MOVE_COLUMN_THEN_ABORT'),(97,100,'General',51,'1.00','2013-09-25 00:00:00','Add search operator in head column',NULL,NULL,'SRX',3,'2013-09-27 06:21:21',NULL),(98,100,'display',51,'1.00','2013-09-26 00:00:00','Improve column contextual with help link',NULL,NULL,'SRX',3,'2013-09-26 14:43:12',NULL);
